(50, 'soap', 'adventure;drama;fantasy', 'Lost', 'Арал', 'lost-2004', '201411', '491471d4e7b47bda7daa75cc6a153e89e1bd368d.jpg', 2004, 2010, 'The survivors of a plane crash are forced to work together in order to survive on a seemingly deserted tropical island.', 'After a mysterious and bloody airplane crash, 48 survivors are left stranded on a Pacific Island... miles off course. It soon becomes apparent that they will not have to cope only with the forces of nature, but with the island''s secrets, including the Dharma Initiative, the ''Lost Numbers'', the "others" (or hostiles) and the strange black smoke- to name a few. There is also much more than meets the eye, as it becomes apparent that everyone is connected in some way and that everyone has a purpose to live on the island... and for some, to die.', 'Онгоцны ослоос амьд үлсэн хэсэг хүмүүс эзгүй арал дээр амьдрахын төлөө хүчээ нэгтгэнэ.', 'Учир битүүлэг, аймшигт ослоос 48 хүн амьд үлдэж, алс холын эзгүй арал дээр орхигдоно. Амьд үлдэхийн төлөө тэмцэл ийнхүү эхэлдэг. Гэвч тэд зөвхөн байгалийн үзэгдэл, амьтадтай тулалдахгүй. Арал өөр олон нууцыг хадгалдаг. Энэ бүхэн алдагдсан хүмүүст аюул занал дагуулна. Хачирхалтай нь арал дээрх хүмүүс ямар нэгэн байдлаар хоорондоо холбоотой, зайлшгүй амьд үлдэх шалтгаантай.', '<iframe width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/0HQLeAnhGYU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0411008" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0411008/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Lost (2004–2010) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 44, 13, 'Bad Robot, Touchstone Television, ABC Studios', 'J.J. Abrams, Jeffrey Lieber, Damon Lindelof', 'J.J. Abrams, Jeffrey Lieber, Damon Lindelof', 6, 96, 'https://www.facebook.com/LOST', 'http://abc.go.com/shows/lost', '2004-09-22', 'Jorge Garcia, Naveen Andrews, Matthew Fox', 'http://kickass.to/usearch/lost/', 0, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'http://abc.go.com/shows/lost', 1, 1, '2014-11-09 11:55:40', '2014-11-09 11:55:40'),
(51, 'soap', 'drama;mystery', 'House M.D.', 'Хаус М.Д', 'house-m-d-2004', '201411', '21ae68f967af958b86a0450fa9ab33284fac7b73.jpg', 2004, 2012, 'An antisocial maverick doctor who specializes in diagnostic medicine does whatever it takes to solve puzzling cases that come his way using his crack team of doctors and his wits.', 'The series follows the life of anti-social, pain killer addict, witty and arrogant medical doctor Gregory House with only half a muscle in his right leg. He and his team of medical doctors try to cure very ill ordinary people in the United States of America.', 'Тэрсүү үзэлт оношилгооны эмч хэсэг нөхдийн хамтаар учир нь олдохгүй, хамгийн төвөгтэй тохиолдлуудыг судалж эхэлнэ.', 'Грегори Хаус бол ухаалаг боловч их зантай хүн. Тэр нийгмээс хол, зожиг амьдралтай. Өвчин намдаах эмэнд донтсон. Бас баруун хөлөндөө тал булчинтай. Гэвч тэр мэргэжил нэгт найзуудтайгаа хамтран АНУ-ын хамгийн энгийн мөртлөө хамгийн хүнд өвчин туссан хүмүүсийг эмчлэхийг оролдоно.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/AifiouvIylM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0412142" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0412142/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="House M.D. (2004–2012) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 44, 13, 'Heel & Toe Films, Shore Z Productions, Bad Hat Harry Productions', 'David Shore', 'David Shore', 8, 177, 'https://www.facebook.com/House', 'http://www.usanetwork.com/house', '2004-01-01', 'Hugh Laurie, Omar Epps, Robert Sean Leonard', 'http://kickass.to/usearch/house%20m.d.', 0, 4, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.usanetwork.com/house', 1, 1, '2014-11-09 12:00:03', '2014-11-09 12:00:03'),
(52, 'movie', 'crime;drama', 'The Shawshank Redemption', 'Шаушенкээс оргосон нь', 'the-shawshank-redemption-1994', '201411', '4f4d37222b85fac418f0883156bc6dd1b38e203a.jpg', 1994, 0000, 'Andy Dufresne is a young and successful banker whose life changes drastically when he is convicted and sentenced to life imprisonment for the murder of his wife and her lover. Set in the 1940''s, the film shows how Andy, with the help of his friend Red, the prison entrepreneur, turns out to be a most unconventional prisoner.', 'In 1946, a banker named Andy Dufresne (Tim Robbins) is convicted of a double murder, even though he stubbornly proclaims his innocence. He''s sentenced to a life term at the Shawshank State Prison in Maine, where another lifer, Ellis Red Redding (Morgan Freeman), picks him as the new recruit most likely to crack under the pressure. The ugly realities of prison life are quickly introduced to Andy: a corrupt warden (Bob Gunton), sadistic guards led by Capt. Byron Hadley (Clancy Brown), and inmates who are little better than animals, willing to use rape or beatings to insure their dominance. But Andy does not crack: he has the hope of the truly innocent, which (together with his smarts) allow him to prevail behind bars. He uses his banking skills to win favor with the warden and the guards, doing the books for Norton''s illegal business schemes and keeping an eye on the investments of most of the prison staff. In exchange, he is able to improve the prison library and bring some dignity and respect back to many of the inmates, including Red. Based on a story by Stephen King, The Shawshank Redemption was the directorial debut of screenwriter Frank Darabont.~ Mark Deming, All Movie Guide', 'Залуухан, дэвжиж явсан банкир Энди Дуфрейний амьдрал нэг л шөнийн дотор орвонгоороо эргэж, эхнэрийнхээ үхэлд хилсээр буруутгагдан, шоронгийн хаалга татдаг. Бүх насаараа хоригдох ял авсан Энди Шаушенкийн шоронд орсон бүх ялтнаас ялгаатай.', '1946 онд Энди Дуфрейн эхнэрийгээ нууц амрагийнх нь хамт буудан хороосон хэргээр бүх насаараа хоригдох ял сонсоно. Энди удалгүй шоронгийн амьдралын хар бараантай танилцана. Хээл хахууль, хүчирхийлэл, харгислал шоронгийн өнцөг булан бүрт бий. Гэсэн ч Энди бууж өгөхгүй. Түүний сэтгэлийн гүнд хэн ч хулгайлж, үгүйсгэж, бузарлаж чадахгүй тийм л хэсэг бий. Энэ бол гэм зэмгүй хүний итгэл найдвар, түүнээс гарах сэтгэлийн тэнхээ юм.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/6hB3S9bIaco" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0111161" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0111161/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Shawshank Redemption (1994) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 142, 12, 'Castle Rock Entertainment', 'Frank Darabont', 'Stephen King, Frank Darabont', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/ShawshankRedemptionFilm', 'https://www.facebook.com/ShawshankRedemptionFilm', '1994-10-14', 'Tim Robbins, Morgan Freeman, Bob Gunton', 'http://kickass.to/usearch/The%20Shawshank%20Redemption/', 0, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/ShawshankRedemptionFilm', 2, 2, '2014-11-09 12:31:28', '2014-12-12 13:12:32'),
(53, 'series', 'crime;drama', 'The Godfather', 'Загалмайлсан эцэг', 'the-godfather-1972', '201411', '0819a5540c91ff6ac0def45f7b6b10e242274b9e.jpg', 1972, 0000, 'The aging patriarch of an organized crime dynasty transfers control of his clandestine empire to his reluctant son.', 'The story begins as "Don" Vito Corleone, the head of a New York Mafia "family", oversees his daughter''s wedding with his wife Carmela. His beloved son Michael has just come home from the war, but does not intend to become part of his father''s business. Through Michael''s life the nature of the family business becomes clear. The business of the family is just like the head of the family, kind and benevolent to those who give respect, but given to ruthless violence whenever anything stands against the good of the family. Don Vito lives his life in the way of the old country, but times are changing and some don''t want to follow the old ways and look out for community and "family". An up and coming rival of the Corleone family wants to start selling drugs in New York, and needs the Don''s influence to further his plan. The clash of the Don''s fading old world values and the new ways will demand a terrible price, especially from Michael, all for the sake of the family.', 'Мафийн бүлэглэлийн толгойлогч эрх мэдлээ бага хүүдээ хүслийг нь үл харгалзан өвлүүлэхээр шийднэ.', 'Дон Вито Карлеоне гэх Нью-Йоркийн мафийн гэр бүлийн толгойлогчийн охины хуримаар кино эхэлдэг. Мафийн гэр бүлд эртнийх гэмээр нэгэн дүрэм үйлчилдэг. Хүндэтгэл үзүүлсэн хэнбугай ч толгойлогчийн өршөөл хайрыг хүртэнэ. Харин гэр бүлийн эсрэг зогсвол, гэмт хэргийн ертөнцийн харгис хатуу хэнийг ч тойрч гарахгүй. Дон Корлеоне хуучин дүрмийг дагадаг. Гэтэл хувьсан өөрчлөгдөх гэмт хэргийн ертөнцөд түүний нөлөө, төлөвлөгөөг үл хүндэтгэх шинэ цэргүүд тасрахгүй. Эцгийнхээ ажлыг өвлөн авсан Майкл ноёрхлоо баталгаажуулахын тулд том золиос гаргахаас аргагүй. Бүх зүйл гэр бүлийн сайн сайхны төлөө байдаг.', '<iframe width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/5DO-nDW43Ik" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0068646" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0068646/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Godfather (1972) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 175, 13, 'Paramount Pictures, Alfran Productions', 'Francis Ford Coppola', 'Mario Puzo, Francis Ford Coppola', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/thegodfather', 'http://www.thegodfather.com', '1994-03-24', 'Marlon Brando, Al Pacino, James Caan', 'http://kickass.to/usearch/The%20Godfather/', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.thegodfather.com', 2, 2, '2014-11-09 13:18:32', '2014-12-12 13:11:46'),
(54, 'series', 'crime;drama', 'The Godfather: Part II', 'Загалмайлсан эцэг: 2-р анги', 'the-godfather-part-ii-1974', '201411', '6724534d80df69517942db92fdd1e8acae2e6780.jpg', 1974, 0000, 'The early life and career of Vito Corleone in 1920s New York is portrayed while his son, Michael, expands and tightens his grip on his crime syndicate stretching from Lake Tahoe, Nevada to pre-revolution 1958 Cuba.', 'The continuing saga of the Corleone crime family tells the story of a young Vito Corleone growing up in Sicily and in 1910s New York; and follows Michael Corleone in the 1950s as he attempts to expand the family business into Las Vegas, Hollywood and Cuba.', '1920-иод оны үеийн Нью-Йорк хотод Вито Корлеонегийн залуугийн амьдрал, ажил хэргийг  1958 оны Кубын хувьсгалаас өмнөх үед Витогийн хүү Майкл Тахой нуураас Невада хүртэлх гэмт хэргийн эзэнт гүрнээ хэрхэн тэлсэн түүхийг нэгэн зэрэг өгүүлнэ.', 'Киноны үргэлжлэл ангид Корлеонегийн удмын мафийн бүлэглэлийн эхлэл ба 1950-иад оны үед Майкл Корлеоне гэр бүлийн бизнесээ Ласвегас, Холливуд, Куба хүртэл өргөжүүлсэн түүхийг өгүүлнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/qJr92K_hKl0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0071562" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0071562/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Godfather: Part II (1974) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 200, 13, 'Paramount Pictures, The Coppola Company', 'Francis Ford Coppola', 'Francis Ford Coppola, Mario Puzo', 0, 0, 'http