(56, 'movie', 'crime;drama;thriller', 'Pulp Fiction', 'Хямд зохиол', 'pulp-fiction-1994', '201411', '3dcb1b12302ede833a7337e6f7d79e927b47cd23.jpg', 1994, 0000, 'The lives of two mob hit men, a boxer, a gangster''s wife, and a pair of diner bandits intertwine in four tales of violence and redemption.', 'Jules Winnfield and Vincent Vega are two hitmen who are out to retrieve a suitcase stolen from their employer, mob boss Marsellus Wallace. Wallace has also asked Vincent to take his wife Mia out a few days later when Wallace himself will be out of town. Butch Coolidge is an aging boxer who is paid by Wallace to lose his next fight. The lives of these seemingly unrelated people are woven together comprising of a series of funny, bizarre and uncalled-for incidents.', 'Хөлсний алуурчин байсан хоёр хүн, нэг боксчин, гэмт хэрэгтний эхнэр, дээрмийн бүлгийн хэсэг хүмүүст тохиолдсон хөгжилтэй, хачирхалтай, санаандгүй үйл явдлууд өрнөнө.', 'Юлис Виннифелд, Винсент Вега хоёр хуучин босс Марселлус Воллосын алдагдсан цүнхийг олох ажил авна. Винсентийн эхнэр Миа энэ хэрэгт оролцоно. Батч Күлидж бол нас ахиж яваа боксчин. Тэр Воллосын заавраар дараагийн тулаандаа ялагдах ёстой. Хоорондоо хамааралгүй мэт эдгээр хүмүүс хоорондоо холбоотой ба холбоогүй үйл явдлуудаар холбогдоно.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/vzeec59Acnk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0110912" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0110912/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Pulp Fiction (1994) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 154, 13, 'Miramax Films, A Band Apart, Jersey Films', 'Quentin Tarantino', 'Quentin Tarantino (story), Roger Avary (story)', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/PulpFiction', 'http://www.miramax.com/movie/pulp-fiction/', '1994-10-01', 'John Travolta, Uma Thurman, Samuel L. Jackson', 'http://kickass.to/usearch/Pulp%20Fiction/', 0, 8, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.miramax.com/movie/pulp-fiction/', 1, 1, '2014-11-09 13:39:55', '2014-11-09 13:39:55'),
(57, 'movie', 'comedy', 'Saving Christmas', '', 'saving-christmas-2014', '201411', '9a91f98bbbd5ec9fd9159cd705fbc1ed85902b08.jpg', 2014, 0000, 'Kirk is enjoying the annual Christmas party extravaganza thrown by his sister until he realizes he needs to help out Christian, his brother-in-law who has a bad case of the bah-humbugs', 'Kirk is enjoying the annual Christmas party extravaganza thrown by his sister until he realizes he needs to help out Christian, his brother-in-law who has a bad case of the bah-humbugs. Kirk''s fresh look at Christmas provides Christian the chance to see Christ is where He has always been: at the center of our Christmas celebrations and traditions', 'иймэрхүү христийн киног оруулаад яахиймбээ, энийг устгаяаа', '', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/z5-yA66kaVc" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '', 80, 13, 'Samuel Goldwyn Films,Provident Films', 'Darren Doane', 'Darren Doane, Cheston Hervey', 0, 0, 'http://www.savingchristmas.com/', 'http://www.savingchristmas.com/', '2014-11-14', 'Kirk Cameron, Darren Doane, Bridgette Cameron', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-11 05:06:18', '2014-11-11 05:06:18'),
(58, 'movie', 'crime;mystery', 'The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo', 'Луугийн шивээстэй охин', 'the-girl-with-the-dragon-tattoo-2011', '201411', 'ab038107aa05c48a42a707a2f1583e22d05db390.jpg', 2011, 0000, 'Journalist Mikael Blomkvist is aided in his search for a woman who has been missing for forty years by Lisbeth Salander, a young computer hacker.', 'This English-language adaptation of the Swedish novel by Stieg Larsson follows a disgraced journalist, Mikael Blomkvist (Daniel Craig), as he investigates the disappearance of a wealthy patriarch''s niece from 40 years ago. He is aided by the pierced, tattooed, punk computer hacker named Lisbeth Salander (Rooney Mara). As they work together in the investigation, Blomkvist and Salander uncover immense corruption beyond anything they have ever imagined.', 'Сэтгүүлч Михайл Вломквист 40 жилийн турш сураггүй алга болсон бүсгүйг эрэх ажилдаа залуу хакер бүсгүй Лисбет Саландераас тусламж хүснэ.', 'Шведийн саятан 40 жилийн өмнө өөд болсон зээ дүүгээ хайлгах ажилд сэтгүүлчийн ажлаа шившигт хутгасан Михайл Бломквистыг хөлсөлнө. Харин Михайл ажилдаа туслуулахаар панк стильтэй, шивээс ээмгээр гоёх дуртай залуухан хакер бүсгүйг олдог. Гэвч тэдний эрлийн ажил үргэлжлэх тусам хээл хахууль, аллагын хэрэг улам л төвөгтэй болж эхэлдэг.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/DqQe3OrsMKI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt1568346" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1568346/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo (2011) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 158, 16, 'Columbia,Metro Goldwyn Mayer', 'David Fincher', 'Steven Zaillian,Stieg Larsson', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/DragonTattoo', 'http://www.dragontattoo.com/site/', '2011-12-21', 'Daniel Craig, Rooney Mara, Christopher Plummer', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 'http://www.dragontattoo.com/site/', 1, 1, '2014-11-11 05:16:01', '2014-11-11 05:16:01'),
(59, 'movie', 'thriller', 'African Gothic', 'Африк маягийн гот', 'african-gothic-2014', '201411', 'c17f70f5c0a19e62e6f7f2b959b0c981a560e92b.jpg', 2014, 0000, 'On an isolated farm in Apartheid South Africa two lovers find themselves at risk of losing everything to a big city lawyer; they will stop at nothing to prevent him from exposing a dark family secret.', 'A couple, isolated on a farm in South Africa, cut off from the world both physically and emotionally, pass their time reenacting their horrific past- role playing in an attempt to erase it. A stranger pays them a visit, only to become part of the madness.', 'Өмнөд Африкийн алслагдсан ферм дээр залуу хосууд байгаа бүхнээ нэгэн хуульчид алдах гэж байгаагаа ойлгоно. Тэд гэр бүлийнхээ хамгийн бохир нууцыг алдахгүйн тулд бүхнийг хийнэ.', 'Өмнөд Африкийн алслагдсан ферм дээр залуу гэр бүл орчин үеийн амьдралаас бие сэтгэлийн хувьд бүрэн тасарсан байдалтай амьдардаг. Тэд өнгөрсөн амьдралынхаа хар бараан хэсгийг эргэн дурсахдаа дүрд хувирч тоглоно. Энэ тэдний цаг хугацааг өнгөрөөх хамгийн гол арга нь юм. Тэднийд зочилж ирсэн танихгүй хүн тэдний энэ солиорлын нэг хэсэг болж хувирна.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/YscH8QR5hhc" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt1931378" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1931378/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="African Gothic (2014) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 90, 16, 'Toronto Int. African Film and Music Festival', 'Gabriel Bologna',