(63, 'movie', 'drama', 'Beyond the Lights', 'Их гэрлийн чанадад', 'beyond-the-lights-2014', '201411', 'd4e0d3fd7dc623aed0eaa6570c5da53883711b6d.jpg', 2014, 0000, 'A talented young musician on the brink of super stardom struggles with the pressure of her new-found success.', 'The pressures of fame have superstar singer Noni on the edge, until she meets Kaz, a young cop who works to help her find the courage to develop her own voice and break free to become the artist she was meant to be.', 'Авъяаслаг дуучин бүсгүй жинхэнэ од болоход ойрхон ирсэн ч гэнэтийн энэ амжилтаас ирэх дарамтыг тэсэж гарахад хэцүү болно.', 'Дуучин бүсгүй Каз хэмээх залуу цагдаатай танилцсанаар өөрийн хүссэнээр замнах зориг зүрхтэй нэгэн болдог.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/5-NsI8lZ5Lw" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt3125324" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3125324/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Beyond the Lights (2014) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 116, 16, 'Relativity', 'Gina Prince-Bythewood', 'Gina Prince-Bythewood', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/BeyondTheLightsMovie', 'https://twitter.com/beyondthelights', '2014-11-14', 'Gugu Mbatha-Raw, Nate Parker, Minnie Driver', '', 0, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-11 06:22:28', '2014-11-11 06:22:28'),
(64, 'series', 'comedy', 'Dumb and Dumber To', 'Тэнэгүүд тэнэгтсэн нь', 'dumb-and-dumber-to-2014', '201411', 'b89478179aa2a46429a80f1d4162cdb8ff30bc28.jpg', 2014, 0000, '20 years since their first adventure, Harry finds out he has a daughter who was adopted. Lloyd and Harry try to find Harry''s adopted daughter.', 'It''s been 20 years and Harry Dunn has found something out....he has a daughter Lloyd Christmas his equally dim witted friend takes one look at a picture of her develops a crush and insists the two track her down what ensues when Harry finally agrees is a bizzare encounter with an old lady and more hilarity in the form of their sheer stupidity', 'Харри нэг л өдөр өөрийгөө хүнд өргүүлсэн охинтой гэдгээ мэднэ. Үл таних охин нь хэдийнээ 20 настай. Харри, Лойд хоёр охиныг олох аялалд гарна.', 'Харригийн тэнэг найз Лойд хүнд өргүүлсэн охины зургийг анх хараад л шууд дурлана. Тиймээс Харриг ятгасаар охиныг олох аялалд тэд хамтдаа гардаг. Тэдний аялал хачин жигтэй, хөгжилтэй, тэнэг үйл явдлуудаар дүүрэн өрнөнө.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/bIqvQFqPavA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt2096672" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2096672/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Dumb and Dumber To (2014) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 110, 16, 'Universal Pictures, Red Granite Pictures', 'Bobby Farrelly, Peter Farrelly', 'Sean Anders Mike Cerrone,', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/DumbandDumberMovie', 'http://dumbanddum