(82, 'movie', 'horror', 'Exists', 'Гарц', 'exists-2014', '201411', 'e042cf8eeab8d8ec76197a7f2bd9f87237e62a27.jpg', 2014, 0000, 'A group of friends who venture into the remote Texas woods for a party weekend find themselves stalked by Bigfoot.', 'For five friends, it was a chance for a summer getaway- a weekend of camping in the Texas Big Thicket. But visions of a carefree vacation are shattered with an accident on a dark and desolate country road. In the wake of the accident, a bloodcurdling force of nature is unleashed-something not exactly human, but not completely animal- an urban legend come to terrifying life...and seeking murderous revenge.', 'Техасын ойд үдэшлэг зохиож, хөгжилдөхөөр шийдсэн хэсэг найзууд Алмасын мөр олно. Алмас тэднийг дагаж байжээ.', 'Таван найз Техасын их ойд амралтаа өнгөрөөх аз таарна. Гэсэн ч ойн замд машин нь эвдэрсэнээр амралтын төлөвлөгөө нь бүхэлдээ нураад зогсохгүй аюулд орно. Хүн гэхэд хүн биш, амьтан гэхэд амьтан биш, үлгэр домгийн аймшигт Алмас тэдний замд гарч ирнэ.', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt1988621" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1988621/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Exists (2014) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt1988621" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1988621/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Exists (2014) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,