(90, 'movie', 'horror', 'The Shining', 'Гялтан', 'the-shining-1980', '201411', '55b07b11d0f333e88cf4d5abd173317192ecd8c9.jpg', 1980, 0000, 'A family heads to an isolated hotel for the winter where an evil and spiritual presence influences the father into violence, while his psychic son sees horrific forebodings from the past and of the future.', 'Signing a contract, Jack Torrance, a normal writer and former teacher agrees to take care of a hotel which has a long, violent past that puts everyone in the hotel in a nervous situation. While Jack slowly gets more violent and angry of his life, his son, Danny, tries to use a special talent, the "Shining", to inform the people outside about whatever that is going on in the hotel.', 'Алслагдсан газарт байрлах нэгэн зочид буудалд ирсэн нэгэн гэр бүлийн амьдралд сэтгэл сэртхийлгэм үйл явдал тохиолдоно.', 'Зохиолч, багш асан Жэк Торрэнс хар түүхийн ул мөр шингэсэн хуучны нэгэн зочид буудлыг харж хандахаар гарын үсэг зурна. Гэвч зочид буудалд ирсэнээр тэр эхнэр, хүүдээ хэтэрхий харгис зан гаргаж эхэлдэг. Жэкийн зөн билэгтэй хүү Дэнни нь өнгөрсөнд болоод ирээдүйд тохиолдох аймшигт зүйлсийг харж эхэлнэ. Тэрээр эргэн тойрондоо байгаа хүмүүст энэ хараагдсан зочид буудалд юу болоод байгааг ойлгуулах арга бодож олно.', '<iframe width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/5Cb3ik6zP2I" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0081505" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0081505/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Shining (1980) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 146, 18, 'Warner Bros Pictures', 'Stanley Kubrick', 'Stephen King (novel), Stanley Kubrick', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/KubrickShining', 'http://kubrickfilms.warnerbros.com/video_detail/shining/', '1980-05-23', 'Jack Nicholson, Shelley Duvall, Danny Lloyd', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-17 12:02:24', '2014-11-17 12:02:24'),
(91, 'movie', 'horror;scifi', 'Alien', 'Харийнхан', 'alien-1979', '201411', '562029ffc3234b6634b8a2f58d1c98669335d06e.jpg', 1979, 0000, 'The commercial vessel Nostromo receives a distress call from an unexplored planet. After searching for survivors, the crew heads home only to realize that a deadly bioform has joined them.', '"In space, no one can hear you scream." A close encounter of the third kind becomes a Jaws-style nightmare when an alien invades a spacecraft in Ridley Scott''s sci-fi horror classic. On the way home from a mission for the Company, the Nostromo''s crew is woken up from hibernation by the ship''s Mother computer to answer a distress signal from a nearby planet. Capt. Dallas''s (Tom Skerritt) rescue team discovers a bizarre pod field, but things get even stranger when a face-hugging creature bursts out of a pod and attaches itself to Kane (John Hurt). Over the objections of Ripley (Sigourney Weaver), science officer Ash (Ian Holm) lets Kane back on the ship. The acid-blooded incubus detaches itself from an apparently recovered Kane, but an alien erupts from Kane''s stomach and escapes. The alien starts stalking the humans, pitting Dallas and his crew (and cat) against a malevolent killing machine that also has a protector in the nefarious Company.', 'Ностромо нэрт сансрын хөлгийнхөн эзэнгүй гаригаас аврал эрсэн дуу чимээ хүлээн авч, амьд үлдсэн хүмүүсийг хайхаар хөдөлнө. Гэр рүүгээ буцах замдаа тэд үхлийн аюулт био хувирагчийг авч яваагаа мэднэ.', '"Сансарт хэн ч хашгирах чимээг сонсохгүй". Сансрын аялалаа дуусгаж явсан Ностромо хөлөг авралын дохиогоор нэгэн гаригт газардана. Хачирхалтай энэ гариг дээр байх үед багийн гишүүн Кэйний нүүрэнд хачин зүйл наалдаж орхидог. Хөлгийн эрдэмтэн Эшийн хүсэлтээр Кэйнийг хөлөгт буцаан суулгахаар шийднэ. Эш Кэйний биеэс харийн биетийг салгаж чадсан ч хадгалж чадалгүй алдсанаар багийнхны хувьд жинхэнэ хар дарсан зүүд эхэлнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/DGAHtWV7Ua8" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0078748" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0078748/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Alien (1979) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 117, 18, 'Twentieth Century-Fox Productions', 'Ridley Scott', 'Dan O''Bannon (story), Ronald Shusett', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/aliendvd', 'https://www.facebook.com/aliendvd', '1979-06-22', 'Sigourney Weaver, Tom Skerritt, John Hurt', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-17 12:28:40', '2014-11-17 12:28:40'),
(92, 'movie', 'drama;war', 'Flags of Our Fathers', 'Туг мандуулсан баатрууд', 'flags-of-our-fathers-2006', '201411', 'de4dcb574edadacb91235f62cdfc51d2b8d9948b.jpg', 2006, 0000, 'The life stories of the six men who raised the flag at The Battle of Iwo Jima, a turning point in WWII.', 'Battle scenes are intercut with footage of three of the soldiers - played by Ryan Phillipe, Jesse Bradford, and Adam Beach -- who survived the battle going on a goodwill tour of the United States in order to sell war bonds. Many evening they are forced to reenact their famous pose, something each of them finds more and more difficult to do as they suffer from survivor''s guilt. Eastwood frames the story by having one of the men''s grown son (Tom McCarthy) interview his father''s old comrades in order to find out more about what happened to his father. Eastwood followed this film with Letters from Iwo Jima, a second film about the battle of Iwo Jima, but told from the Japanese perspective. Flags of Our Fathers was produced by Eastwood and Steven Spielberg. ~ Perry Seibert, Rovi', 'Дэлхийн хоёрдугаар дайны шийдвэрлэх тулаан өрнөсөн Иво Жимад ялалтын туг мандуулсан зургаан цэргийн амьдралын түүхийг өгүүлнэ.', 'Дэлхийн дайныг шийдсэн баатарлаг тулааны гэрчүүд гэртээ иргэн ирлээ. Тэд АНУ-ыг тойрон аялаж, ялалтын мэдээг хүмүүст хүргэх ажилд томилогдсон ч энэ ажил өдөр ирэх тусам илүү хүнд санагдаж ажээ. Дайнд үрэгдсэн аавынхаа талаар илүү ихийг мэдэхийн хүссэн залуу хүү цэргүүдээс олон зүйл асууна.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/FUjyJjMcNlU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0418689" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0418689/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Flags of Our Fathers (2006) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 110, 16, 'DreamWorks Warner Bros pictures', 'Clint Eastwood', 'William Broyles Jr. (screenplay), Paul Haggis', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/FlagsOfOurFathers', 'http://wwws.warnerbros.fr/flagsofourfathers/', '2006-10-20', 'Ryan Phillippe, Barry Pepper, Joseph Cross', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-18 03:15:09', '2014-11-18 03:15:09'),
(93, 'movie', 'scifi', 'Letters from Iwo Jima', '', 'letters-from-iwo-jima-2006', '201411', 'c2c55afa8e1109428723cbbc3c1210d5dd6520da.jpg', 2006, 0000, 'The story of the battle of Iwo Jima between the United States and Imperial Japan during World War II, as told from the perspective of the Japanese who fought it.', 'In 1945, World War II was in its last stages, and U.S. forces were planning to take on the Japanese on a small island known as Iwo Jima. While the island was mostly rock and volcanoes, it was of key strategic value and Japan''s leaders saw the island as the final opportunity to prevent an Allied invasion. Lt. General Tadamichi Kuribayashi (Ken Watanabe) was put in charge of the forces on Iwo Jima; Kuribayashi had spent time in the United States and was not eager to take on the American army, but he also understood his opponents in a way his superiors did not, and devised an unusual strategy of digging tunnels and deep foxholes that allowed his troops a tactical advantage over the invading soldiers. While Kuribayashi''s strategy alienated some older officers, it impressed Baron Nishi (Tsuyoshi Ihara), the son of a wealthy family who had also studied America firsthand as an athlete at the 1932 Olympics. As Kuribayashi and his men dig in for a battle they are not certain they can win -- and most have been told they will not survive -- their story is told both by watching their actions and through the letters they write home to their loved ones, letters that in many cases would not be delivered until long after they were dead. Among the soldiers manning Japan''s last line of defense are Saigo (Kazunari Ninomiya), a baker sent to Iwo Jima only days before his wife was to give birth; Shimizu (Ryo Kase), who was sent to Iwo Jima after washing out in the military police; and Lieutenant Ito (Shidou Nakamura), who has embraced the notion of "Death Before Surrender" with particular ferocity. Filmed in Japanese with a primarily Japanese cast, Letters From Iwo Jima was shot in tandem with Flags of Our Fathers, and the two films were released within two months of one another', 'Дэлхийн хоёрдугаар дайны үед АНУ, хаант Япон улс Иво Жимад тулалдсан түүхээс сэдэвлэн бүтээсэн кино.', '1945 он, Дэлхийн хоёрдугаар дайны төгсгөл үе. АНУ Япончуудыг Иво Жима нэрт арал дээр цохихоор төлөвлөж байлаа. Харин Япончууд хад чулуу, галт уул ихтэй энэ арлыг Холбоотны хүчнийг буулгаж авах эцсийн боломж гэж үзэв. АНУ-д амьдарч байсан Японы Генерал Тадамичи Курибаяаши дайсны талаар дээд тушаалтнуудаас илүү мэдлэгтэй нэгэн. Тэрээр дайран ирэх цэргүүдээс тактикийн хувьд илүү байрлал эзлэхийн тулд арлын доогуур хонгил гаргах ухаалаг төлөвлөгөө боловсруулна. Ийнхүү хонгил гаргах ажилд томилогдсон цэргүүдийн ар гэртээ бичсэн захидлуудаар кино үргэлжилнэ. Эцсийн тулаан хэрхэн өрнөх талаар сэтгэл зовнин, тулааны дараа амьд үлдэх эсэхээ мэдэхгүй байгаа цэргүүдийн сэтгэл хөдлөл, сүүлчийн үгс захидлаар дамжин гэрт нь хүрэх үед тэд хэдийнээ энэ хорвоогоос явсан байна.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/51lo2dpaZ_g" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0498380" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0498380/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Letters from Iwo Jima (2006) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 141, 16, 'DreamWorks Warner Bros pictures', 'Clint Eastwood', 'Iris Yamashita (screenplay), Iris Yamashita', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Letters-From-Iwo-Jima-Movie/562084490477715', 'http://wwws.warnerbros.co.uk/lettersfromiwojima/lettersofiwojima/framework/framework.html', '2007-02-02', 'Ken Watanabe, Kazunari Ninomiya, Tsuyoshi Ihara', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-18 03:27:37', '2014-11-18 03:27:37'),
(94, 'movie', 'action;drama', 'We Were Soldiers', 'Бид цэрэг явсан', 'we-were-soldiers-2002', '201411', 'd4e9c220761dd8744cf449393672c3b7108a0245.jpg', 2002, 0000, 'The story of the first major battle of the American phase of the Vietnam War and the soldiers on both sides that fought it.', 'In a place soon to be known as The Valley of Death, in a football field-sized clearing called landing zone X-Ray, Lt. Colonel Hal Moore and 400 young troopers from the newly formed 1/7th Cavalry Regiment of the US 1st "Air" Cavalry Division were surrounded by 2,000 North Vietnamese soldiers dug into the tunnel warren mountainside. The ensuing battle was one of the most savage in U.S. history and is portrayed here as the signal encounter between the American and North Vietnamese armies. We Were Soldiers Once... And Young is a tribute to the nobility of those men under fire, their common acts of uncommon valor, and their loyalty to and love for one another.', 'Вьетнамын дайнд мордсон Америкийн цэргүүд хамгийн анхны дайралтыг хийсэн бодит түүхийг өгүүлэх кино.', 'Ихкс-Рэй хэмээн нэрлэсэн хөлбөмбөгийн талбайн хэмжээтэй нэгэн хөндийд Хурандаа Хал Мур 400 залуу цэргийн хамтаар газардана. Гэвч тэд хойд Вьетнамын 2000 цэргийн бүслэлтэд орсоноо мэдээгүй байжээ. Америк, Вьетнам цэргүүдийн нүүр тулсан томоохон тулаануудын нэгд тооцогдох энэ уулзалт АНУ-ын түүхэнд хамгийн харгис тулаан хэмээн бичигдэж, тэдний тулалдсан газрыг Үхлийн хөндий гэж нэрлэх болсон юм. Залуу насны ид хаваа гайхуулан эрэлхэгээр тулалдаж, амь үрэгдсэн цэргүүдийн дурсгалд зориулан энэ киног бүтээжээ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/h0yUlbAt8Kk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0277434" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0277434/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="We Were Soldiers (2002) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 138, 16, 'Paramount Icon Production', 'Randall Wallace', 'Harold G. Moore (book), Joseph L. Galloway', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/WeWereSoldiersFilm', 'http://www.weweresoldiers.net/', '2002-03-01', 'Mel Gibson, Madeleine Stowe, Greg Kinnear', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-18 07:20:16', '2014-11-18 07:20:16'),
(95, 'movie', 'action;drama;romance', 'Pearl Harbor', 'Сувдан эрэг', 'pearl-harbor-2001', '201411', '94ab867d9913ef913afbc1da05af0b8fafb20b0d.jpg', 2001, 0000, 'Pearl Harbor follows the story of two best friends, Rafe and Danny, and their love lives as they go off to join the war.', 'Pearl Harbor is a classic tale of romance set during a war that complicates everything. It all starts when childhood friends Rafe and Danny become Army Air Corps pilots and meet Evelyn, a Navy nurse. Rafe falls head over heels and next thing you know Evelyn and Rafe are hooking up. Then Rafe volunteers to go fight in Britain and Evelyn and Danny get transferred to Pearl Harbor. While Rafe is off fighting everything gets completely whack and next thing you know everybody is in the middle of an air raid we now know as "Pearl Harbo', 'Дайнд мордсон залуу хоёр нисгэгч, тэдний хайр дурлал ба дэлхийн хоёрдугаар дайнд АНУ-г татагдан ороход хүргэсэн Сувдан эргийн гунигт түүхийг өгүүлнэ.', 'Зэвсэгт хүчний агаарын цэргийн албанд татагдсан хоёр нисгэгч найзууд Рэйф, Дэнни хоёр залуу үзэсгэлэнт сувилагч бүсгүй Эвиленд дурлана. Рэйф урьтан хөдөлж, залуу бүсгүйн сэтгэлийг татсанаар тэд үерхэж эхэлдэг. Гэсэн ч удалгүй Рэйф Англи руу дайнд сайн дураар мордож, Дэнни, Эвилен хоёр Сувдан Эрэг рүү хуваарилагдана. Рэйфийн суманд өртөж, ор сураггүй алга болсон мэдээ ирэхэд, үлдэж хоцорсон хоёр бие биеэ тайвшруулна.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/oGYcxjywx0o" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0213149" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0213149/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Pearl Harbor (2001) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.imag