(105, 'movie', '', 'Night and the City', 'Шөнийн хот', 'night-and-the-city-1992', '201411', 'f1b8c4b8911f2fee0aca658110ffd582263864d9.jpg', 1992, 0000, 'The story about a cheating and incompetent lawyer (Harry Fabian) who suddenly gets obsessed on becoming a boxing promoter.', 'Night and the City is a remake of the 1950 Richard Widmark vehicle of the same name. Major changes: As played by Robert DeNiro, the Widmark character, one Harry Fabian, is no longer merely a two-bit tout but instead a two-bit lawyer; and the film is set in New York, as opposed to the London setting of the original. While embroiled in a lawsuit involving a boxer, Fabian becomes fascinated in the world of championship prizefights. Always susceptible to get-rich-quick schemes, Fabian tries to organize his own big boxing event, but to do that he needs the help of hardnosed promoter Alan King--and to get to King, Fabian uses the promoter''s father, former boxer Jack Warden, to act as front man. Fabian scurries around lying and double-dealing in order to sell percentages of the upcoming bout, while King warns Fabian of the consequences should anything unfortunate happen to the ailing Warden. Disaster plagues Fabian as his boxers fail to pass their physicals, and Warden dies while setting up the big event. Pursued by King and his creditors, the terrified Fabian is urged by girlfriend Jessica Lange to get of town. Instead, Fabian decides to face up to his failings for the first time in his life, and stands his ground for the final, fatal confrontation. Like the earlier Widmark film, the 1992 Night and the City is based on a novel by Gerald Kersh.', 'Луйварчин, мэргэжилдээ муу хуульч боксчдод хөрөнгө оруулахаар шийднэ.', '1950 оны киноны шинэчилсэн хувилбар. Хуучин кино нь Лондон хотын энгийн наймаачин залуугийн оронд Нью-Йорк хотын хуульч гарна. Хялбар аргаар мөнгө олох хүсэлтэй Фабиан хувийн боксын тэмцээн зохион байгуулж, бооцооны мөнгөөр баяжихаар шийднэ. Ингээд энэ төлөвлөгөөндөө Алан Кингийг туслуулахаар урхидна. Тэмцээний бооцоог өсгөхийн тулд худал хэлэх, хуйвалдаан зохион байгуулах ажлыг тун ч шаламгай хийнэ. Гэтэл гай газар доороос гэгчээр тэмцээнд орох боксчин бэлтгэлийн хүндийг даалгүй өөд болно. Үүнийг мэдсэн Кинг Фабианыг сүрдүүлдэг. Фабианы найз бүсгүй Жессика нөхцөл байдлаас зугтааж, хотоос явах санал гаргана. Гэвч Фабиан амьдралдаа анх удаа зугтаах биш, бодит байдалтай нүүр тулж, тэмцэх сонголт хийнэ.', '<iframe width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/d1NmpF0M4SM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0105001" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0105001/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Night and the City (1992) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 105, 16, 'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation', 'Irwin Winkler', 'Gerald Kersh (novel), Richard Price', 0, 0, '', '', '1993-01-01', 'Robert De Niro, Jessica Lange, Cliff Gorman', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-19 04:20:50', '2014-11-19 04:20:50'),
(106, 'soap', 'comedy;drama;mystery', 'Desperate Housewives', 'Яахаас ч буцахгүй эзэгтэй нэр', 'desperate-housewives-2004', '201411', '16e83461145098bbdbf3f77534434840f2aa3546.jpg', 2004, 2012, 'Secrets and truths unfold through the lives of female friends in one suburban neighborhood, after the mysterious suicide of a neighbor.', 'The "normal" suburban life for a group of close-knit housewives takes a dark turn when one of their closest friends mysteriously commits suicide. Now while trying to deal with their own hectic problems and romantic lives, each year brings on a new mystery and more dark and twisted events to come. Life behind closed doors is about to be revealed as suburban life takes a funny and dark turn.', 'Хотын захын нэгэн хороололд амьдардаг хөрш найз бүсгүйчүүдийн амьдралд бие биедээ итгэж дэлгэх үнэн их байдаг ч, цөхрөлтгүй далдлахаар хичээх нууц ч бас бий.', 'Хотын захын хорооллын тайван амьдралтай хөршүүд олон жилийн туршид найз нөхөд болцгооно. Гэвч бүсгүйчүүдийн нэг "нууцлаг байдлаар" амиа хорлосноор эндэхийн амьдралд өөр олон үйл явдал дагуулна. Хүн бүр хувьдаа асуудалтай, жил бүр шинэ нууц гарч ирнэ. Эзэгтэй нарын амьдрал эрээнтэй, бараантай.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/rAbKBUJ4NRY" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0410975" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0410975/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Desperate Housewives (2004–2012) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 45, 13, 'Cherry Alley Productions, Cherry Productions, Touchstone Television', 'Marc Cherry', 'Marc Cherry', 8, 200, 'http://abc.go.com/shows', 'http://www.canalplus.fr/c-series/pid4291-c-desperate-housewives.html', '2004-01-05', 'Teri Hatcher, Felicity Huffman, Marcia Cross', 'http://kickass.so/desperate-housewives-season-1-2-3-4-5-6-7-8-extras-dvdr-t7750903.html', 0, 12, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.canalplus.fr/c-series/pid4291-c-desperate-housewives.html', 2, 2, '2014-11-19 08:20:48', '2014-12-12 13:07:21'),
(107, 'soap', 'comedy;romance', 'Sex and the City', 'Их хотын амьдрал ба секс', 'sex-and-the-city-1998', '201411', '80835ca4ee7f2b419dc34eec61d8716293d83abb.jpg', 1998, 2004, 'The show follows the lives of a group of four women—three in their mid-thirties and one in her forties—who, despite their different natures and ever-changing sex lives, remain inseparable and confide in each other. Starring Sarah Jessica Parker (as Carrie Bradshaw), Kim Cattrall (as Samantha Jones), Kristin Davis (as Charlotte York), and Cynthia Nixon (as Miranda Hobbes), the quirky series had multiple continuing storylines that tackled relevant and modern social issues such as sexuality, safe sex, promiscuity, and femininity while exploring the difference between friendships and romantic relationships.', 'Carrie Bradshaw is a charming petite columnist, and often the narrator of the story, either writing her copy or off screen, constantly tossing up and rejecting different views on just about anything that does or might impact modern women''s sex lives; she tries almost everything, is constantly disappointed, but always seems to return to a certain Mr. Big. Miranda Hobbes is a red-hair lawyer determined to score professionally and to be tough in love to, yet her only faithful lover is an insecure nerd. Charlotte York is a gallery-managing wasp from a prestigious, super-rich family, with high old-fashioned moral standards for her lovable but insecure self but unfortunately almost impossible to live up to for any lover, whenever she can find a socially acceptable one. Samantha Jones is every feminist''s hero, and the utterly unashamed voice of lust at their meetings: an acclaimed PR agent and unstoppable nymphomaniac man-eater who can flirt the pants off almost any man (often literally and fast) and always feels like more, without a hint of commitment, claiming this is the age for woman to do what men always did to them.', 'Зан төлөвийн хувьд ялгаатай, сексийн амьдрал нь ч өөр 4 бүсгүй танилцаж, бат бөх нөхөрлөл үүсгэнэ. Тэдэнд хайр дурлал, болзоо, секс, ажил, загвар, мөнгө гээд л ярихгүй сэдэв байхгүй.', 'Кэрри бол дур булаам бяцхан бүсгүй. Тэр нийтлэлчийн ажил хийдэг. Эмэгтэйчүүдийн сексийн амьдрал, үзэл бодол, хайр дурлалын талаар үзэл бодлоо бичих дуртай. Түүний хайр дурлалын амьдрал ярвигтай ч үргэлж л Том Ноёнтонтой уулзаж төгсдөг. Миранда Хобс бол чадварлаг хуульч бүсгүй. Тэр хайр дурлалд ч бас яс тас, мэргэжлийн байхыг хүсдэг. Гэвч түүний үнэнч амраг нь дэндүү энгийн нэгэн. Шарлот Йорк энэ хотын хамгийн баян, нэр хүндтэй гэр бүлээс гаралтай. Бүсгүй ёс суртахууны маш хуучинсаг зарчмуудыг баримтлах тул түүний шаардлагад нийцэх хүн олоход хэцүү. Саманта Жөүнс PR-ын чиглэлээр мэргэшсэн маркетер бүсгүй. Тэрээр ямарч эр хүний өмдийг тайлах чадалтай. Бас сексийн дуусашгүй их хүсэл тачаалтай.', '<iframe width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/y6U8o9Ed0VI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0159206" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0159206/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Sex and the City (1998–2004) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 30, 18, 'Darren Star Productions, Home Box Office (HBO), Sex and the City', 'Darren Star', 'Candace Bushnell', 6, 94, 'http://www.hbo.com/sex-and-the-city', 'http://www.hbo.com/sex-and-the-city', '1998-01-01', 'Sarah Jessica Parker, Kim Cattrall, Kristin Davis', 'http://kickass.so/sex-and-the-city-seasons-1-2-3-4-5-6-subtitles-extras-t1228140.html', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.hbo.com/sex-a