(108, 'soap', 'comedy;drama;romance', 'The O.C.', 'О.С', 'the-o-c-2004', '201411', 'a3b638bfd580ba7257dfefb1c73a46028f85b475.jpg', 2004, 2007, 'A troubled youth becomes embroiled in the lives of a close-knit group of people in the wealthy, upper-class neighborhood of Newport Beach, Orange County, California.', 'High school is over. Time to move on. But events conspire to reunite Ryan, Seth and Summer in posh, seaside Newport. And there may even be a new Core Four.', 'Калифорниа мужийн Оранж дүүрэгт Ньюпортын эрэг хэмээх баячуудын хороолол бий. Тэндэхийн хүмүүсийн ээдрээтэй амьдралд нэгэн шинэ залуу орж ирнэ.', '10 жилийн сургуулиа төгслөө. Одоо цаашаа яах вэ? Амьдрал аяндаа л Риан, Сэт, Саммер нарыг Ньюпортын эрэг дээр эргэн уулзуулна.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/_PihUdbGsqU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0362359" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0362359/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The O.C. (2003–2007) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 44, 13, 'Wonderland Sound and Vision, Warner Bros. Television, College Hill Pictures Inc.', 'Josh Schwartz', 'Josh Schwartz', 4, 92, 'http://www.channel4.com/programmes/the-oc', 'http://www.channel4.com/programmes/the-oc', '2004-01-01', 'Mischa Barton, Adam Brody, Peter Gallagher', 'http://kickass.so/the-o-c-complete-series-all-episodes-dvdrip-hdtv-t1325337.html', 0, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_O.C.', 2, 2, '2014-11-19 08:50:33', '2014-12-12 13:0