(115, 'soap', 'comedy;drama', 'Jane by Design', '', 'jane-by-design-2011', '201411', '4348b3f6b188312ea04921c06844170660dd2c59.jpg', 2011, 0000, 'A case of mistaken identity has a dateless high school outsider living a double life as a twenty-something career girl in the fashion world.', 'In the introductory season of "Jane by Design", Jane Quimby (Erica Dasher) is a teenager that leads a double life as a high-school student and an assistant to a fashion executive (played by Andie MacDowell .). The comedy-drama picks up on Jane''s struggle to balance both worlds while taking on life''s dramas and maturing. Special appearances from Patricia Field, Stefano Tonchi, and Betsey Johnson among many others from both fashion and design acclaim.', 'Жэйн хоёр төрлийн амьдралтай. Нэг нь 10 жилийн сургуулийн сурагч, нөгөө нь загварын ертөнцийн алдарт дезайнерийн хорин хэдэн настай туслах.', 'Жэйн Квимби 10 жилийн сургуулийн сурагч. Гэвч сургуулиас гадуур дезайнерийн туслахаар ажилладаг. Энэ хоёр амьдралынхаа тэнцвэрийг олох тун ч хэцүү. Учир нь эгд нь насанд хүрсэн хүн, нөгөөд нь өсвөр насны охин байх ёстой.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/otQzYp0x4F4" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt1743904" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1743904/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Jane by Design (2011– ) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 44, 6, 'ABC Family Worldwide', 'April Blair', 'April Blair', 1, 18, 'imdb.com', 'imdb.com', '2011-01-01', '