(116, 'movie', 'biography;drama', 'Milk', 'Милк', 'milk-2008', '201411', '979bfc723c38cf1cba0f1f144ae9d3cb8d231b9c.jpg', 2008, 0000, 'The story of Harvey Milk, and his struggles as an American gay activist who fought for gay rights and became California''s first openly gay elected official.', 'In 1977, Harvey Milk was elected to the San Francisco Board of Supervisors, becoming the first openly gay man to be voted into public office in America. His victory was not just a victory for gay rights; he forged coalitions across the political spectrum. From senior citizens to union workers, Harvey Milk changed the very nature of what it means to be a fighter for human rights and became, before his untimely death in 1978, a hero for all Americans. During the last eight years of his life, while living in New York City, he turns 40. Looking for more purpose, he and his lover Scott Smith relocate to San Francisco, where they found a small business, Castro Camera, in the heart of a working-class neighborhood. Then, with support from Scott and from new friends like young activist Cleve Jones, Milk plunges headfirst into the choppy waters of politics. Bolstering his public profile with humor, Milk''s actions speak even louder than his gift-of-gab words. When Milk is elected supervisor for the newly zoned District 5, he tries to coordinate his efforts with those of another newly elected supervisor, Dan White. But as White and Milk''s political agendas increasingly diverge, their personal destinies tragically converge.', 'Ижил хүйстнүүдийн эрхийг хамгаалах тэмцэгч, Калифорниа мужийн захиргаанд сонгогдсон анхны ил ижил хүйстэн Харви Милкийн түүх.', '1977 онд Харви Милк Сан Франциско хотын захиргааны удирдах албан тушаалд сонгогджээ. Сонгогдохоосоо өмнө тэрээр олон нийтэд бэлгийн чиг хандлагаа мэдэгдсэн төдийгүй ижил хүйстнүүдийн эрхийг хамгаалах тэмцэх тухайгаа зарлаж байжээ. Тэрээр хүний эрхийн төлөөх тэмцэл ямар утгай болохыг Америкчуудад ойлгуулсан бөгөөд 1978 онд нас барахад нь Америкчууд түүний баатар хэмээн үзэж байлаа.', '<iframe width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/Zp0uYT0zDbA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt1013753" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1013753/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Milk (2008) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 128, 13, 'Focus Features', 'Gus Van Sant', 'Dustin Lance Black', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/MilktheMovie', 'http://www.focusfeatures.com/milk', '2009-01-30', 'Sean Penn, Josh Brolin, Emile Hirsch', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-11-20 02:44:55', '2014-12-12 13:05:24');
