(133, 'movie', 'drama', 'One Flew Over the Cuckoo''s Nest', 'Үүрнээсээ ниссэн шувуу', 'one-flew-over-the-cuckoo-s-nest-1975', '201411', '6f3633099f56eb266438c246248345122b7105b5.jpg', 1975, 0000, 'McMurphy has a criminal past and has once again gotten himself into trouble with the law. To escape labor duties in prison, McMurphy pleads insanity and is sent to a ward for the mentally unstable. Once here, McMurphy both endures and stands witness to the abuse and degradation of the oppressive Nurse Ratched, who gains superiority and power through the flaws of the other inmates. McMurphy and the other inmates band together to make a rebellious stance against the atrocious Nurse.', 'There he encounters a motley crew of mostly voluntary inmates, including cowed mama''s boy Billy (Brad Dourif) and silent Native American Chief Bromden (Will Sampson), presided over by the icy Nurse Ratched (Louise Fletcher). Ratched and McMurphy recognize that each is the other''s worst enemy: an authority figure who equates sanity with correct behavior, and a misfit who is charismatic enough to dismantle the system simply by living as he pleases. McMurphy proceeds to instigate group insurrections large and small, ranging from a restorative basketball game to an unfettered afternoon boat trip and a tragic after-hours party with hookers and booze. Nurse Ratched, however, has the machinery of power on her side to ensure that McMurphy will not defeat her. Still, McMurphy''s message to live free or die is ultimately not lost on one inmate, revealing that escape is still possible even from the most oppressive conditions.', 'МкМюрфи урьд нь гэмт хэрэгт холбогдож явсан нэгэн. Дахин нэг удаа хууль зөрчөөд шоронгийн албадан хөдөлмөрөөс зайлсхийж, галзуурсан болж жүжиглэн, сэтгэцийн эмнэлэгт хүргэгдэнэ. Сэтгэцийн эмнэлэгт өвчтнүүд дээрэлхүү зантай, харгис сувилагчийн дарамтыг тэсвэрлэхдээ тэсч, тэрсэлдэхдээ тэмцэлдэн суудаг. Тиймээс Мюрфи болон хэсэг нөхөд нь бослого гаргахаар шийддэг.', 'Мюрфи сэтгэцийн эмнэлэгт удалгүй найз нөхөдтэй болдог. Найз нөхөд нь хүйтэн сэтгэлтэй Рэчид сувилагчийн дарамтанд амьдардаг болохыг мэдсэнээс хойш Мюрфи Рэчид сувилагчтай өстөн дайснууд болно. Рэчид эмх цэгц, ариун цэврээс эхлээд бүгдийг дүрмийн дагуу байлгахыг хүсдэг. Гэтэл Мюрфи ердөө л хүссэнээрээ байхыг хичээдэг. Удалгүй тэр үзэл бодлоо бусаддаа ойлгуулж эхэлсэнээр тэдний дайн улам даамжирна. Сувилагч бүсгүй хамтрагчдынхаа тусламжтайгаар ялагдахгүйн тулд юу ч хийхээс буцахгүй. Харин Мюрфи хамгийн аймшигт нөхцлөөс ч зугтах гэж нэг арга байдгийг батлахыг оролдоно.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2WSyJgydTsA', '', 133, 18, 'Fantasy Films', 'Milos Forman', 'Lawrence Hauben, Bo Goldman', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/OneFlewOverTheCuckoosNestFilm', 'https://www.facebook.com/OneFlewOverTheCuckoosNestFilm', '1975-11-25', 'Michael Berryman, Peter Brocco, Dean R. Brooks, Alonzo Brown', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/OneFlewOverTheCuckoosNestFilm', 1, 1, '2014-11-26 12:06:58', '2014-11-26 12:06:58'),
(134, 'movie', 'drama;romance;war', 'Gone with the Wind', 'Салхиар туугдагсад', 'gone-with-the-wind-1940', '201411', '435ac68180caa5c1165309c8041c8c9e5ca001d8.jpg', 1940, 0000, 'Scarlett is beautiful. She has vitality. But Ashley, the man she has wanted for so long, is going to marry his placid cousin, Melanie. Mammy warns Scarlett to behave herself at the party at Twelve Oaks. There is a new man there that day, the day the Civil War begins. Rhett Butler. Scarlett does not know he is in the room when she pleads with Ashley to choose her instead of Melanie.', 'Gone With the Wind opens in April of 1861, at the palatial Southern estate of Tara, where Scarlett O''Hara (Vivien Leigh) hears that her casual beau Ashley Wilkes (Leslie Howard) plans to marry "mealy mouthed" Melanie Hamilton (Olivia de Havilland). Despite warnings from her father (Thomas Mitchell) and her faithful servant Mammy (Hattie McDaniel), Scarlett intends to throw herself at Ashley at an upcoming barbecue at Twelve Oaks. Alone with Ashley, she goes into a fit of histrionics, all of which is witnessed by roguish Rhett Butler (Clark Gable), the black sheep of a wealthy Charleston family, who is instantly fascinated by the feisty, thoroughly self-centered Scarlett: "We''re bad lots, both of us." The movie''s famous action continues from the burning of Atlanta (actually the destruction of a huge wall left over from King Kong) through the now-classic closing line, "Frankly, my dear, I don''t give a damn." Holding its own against stiff competition (many consider 1939 to be the greatest year of the classical Hollywood studios), Gone With the Wind won ten Academy Awards, including Best Picture, Best Director, Best Screenplay, Best Actress (Vivien Leigh), and Best Supporting Actress (Hattie McDaniel, the first African-American to win an Oscar). The film grossed nearly 192 million dollars, assuring that, just as he predicted, Selznick''s epitaph would be "The Man Who Made Gone With the Wind." ~ Hal Erickson, Rovi', 'Скарлет үзэсгэлэнтэй, сайхан бүсгүй. Тэр үргэлж л эрч хүчээр дүүрэн явдаг. Гэтэл түүний хүсэн хүлээсэн залуу Эшли нь үеэл эгч Меланиетэй нь гэрлэхээр болно. Бууж өгөх дургүй Скарлет гэрлэлтийг болиулах арга сэднэ.', '1861 оны 4-р сар. Өмнөдийн Тарагийн эдлэнгийн залуу гоо бүсгүй Скарлет мөрөөдлийн залуу Эшлигээ өөр хүнтэй суух болсныг сонсоод тэдний гэрлэлтийг зогсоохын тулд Эшлиг эргүүлэх арга хайна. Гэтэл түүний Эшлид хайраа илчилж байгааг Чарлестоны чинээлэг эр Рэт Батлер сонсоно. Ааш муутай, амиа бодсон залуу бүсгүй Рэтийн сэтгэлийг татна. Удалгүй иргэний дайн өрнөж, Скарлет хүнд хэцүү цагийг туулна. Гэвч тэр хэзээ ч бууж өгөхгүй. Харин Рэт Скарлетийг өөрийн болгохын тулд бүхнийг хийнэ.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lrhNPS4nbmQ', '', 238, 6, 'Warner Bros Pictures, Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer', 'Victor Fleming, George Cukor', 'Margaret Mitchell, Sidney Howard', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/GoneWithTheWindOfficial', 'http://www.gonewiththewindmovie.com/', '1978-01-17', 'Clark Gable, Vivien Leigh, Thomas Mitchell', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.gonewiththewindmovie.com/', 1, 1, '2014-11-26 12:26:27', '2014-11-26 12:26:27'),
(135, 'movie', 'drama;mystery', 'Citizen Kane', 'Иргэн Кэйн', 'citizen-kane-1941', '201411', '4c0429870316ba55f6a686699fa80c1436492598.jpg', 1941, 0000, 'Following the death of a publishing tycoon, news reporters scramble to discover the meaning of his final utterance.', 'A group of reporters who are trying to decipher the last word ever spoke by Charles Foster Kane, the millionaire newspaper tycoon: "Rosebud." The film begins with a news reel detailing Kane''s life for the masses, and then from there, we are shown flashbacks from Kane''s life. As the reporters investigate further, the viewers see a display of a fascinating man''s rise to fame, and how he eventually fell off the "top of the world."', 'Хэвлэл мэдээллийн хэрэгслийн гол бай болсон нэгэн хүний гэнэтийн үхэл сурвалжлагч нарыг өөд болоочийн амьдралын тухай гүнзгийрүүлэн судлахад хүргэнэ.', 'Хэвлэлийн гол баатар тэрбумтан Чарлес Фостер Кэйний өөд болохдоо хэлсэн сүүлчийн үгс нь "цоморлигоо нээгээгүй цэцэг" байлаа. Энэ үгс ямар утгатай болохыг мэдэхийг хүссэн хэсэг сэтгүүлчид Кэйний амьдралыг судалж эхэлдэг. Тэд Кэйний нэр алдарын оргилд хэрхэн хүрч, эцэст нь өндөрлөгөөс хэрхэн унасан тухай түүхийг хүмүүст дэлгэнэ.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8dxh3lwdOFw', '', 119, 6, 'Warner Bros Pictures, RKO Radio Pictures', 'Orson Welles', 'Herman J. Mankiewicz, Orson Welles', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/CitizenKaneMovie', 'http://www.warnerbros.com/citizen-kane', '1999-09-05', 'Orson Welles, Joseph Cotten, Dorothy Comingore', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.warnerbros.com/citizen-kane', 1, 1, '2014-11-26 12:44:18', '2014-11-26 12:44:18'),
(136, 'movie', 'adventure;fantasy', 'The Wizard of Oz', 'Өү Зигийн Шидтэн', 'the-wizard-of-oz-1939', '201411', 'e3c08587bc5d175a8ac614c009b313efcc3fb380.jpg', 1939, 0000, 'Dorothy Gale is swept away to a magical land in a tornado and embarks on a quest to see the Wizard who can help her return home.', 'Dorothy and her dog Toto are caught in a tornado''s path and somehow end up in the land of Oz. Here she meets some memorable friends and foes in her journey to meet the Wizard of Oz who everyone says can help her return home and possibly grant her new friends their goals of a brain, heart and courage.', 'Дороти Гэйл хар салхинд хийсч явсаар ид шидийн ертөнцөд хүрч ирнэ. Тэгээд гэртээ буцахад нь туслах шидтэнийг хайх аялалаа эхэлнэ.', 'Өү Зи хэмээх ид шидийн оронд очсон Дороти ба түүний нохой Тото хоёр гэртээ харих замаа хайж явахдаа олон найзтай болдог. Тэд Өү Зигийн шидтэн Доротид гэртээ харихад нь тусалж, харин өөрсдөд нь мэргэн ухаан, сэтгэл зүрх, эр зориг өгнө гэдэгт итгэлтэй байна.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VNugTWHnSfw', '', 102, 3, 'Warner Bros Pictures, Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer', 'Victor Fleming, George Cukor', 'Noel Langley, Florence Ryerson', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/TheWizardOfOzMovie', 'http://thewizardofoz.warnerbros.com/', '1999-08-25', 'Judy Garland, Frank Morgan, Ray Bolger', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://thewizardofoz.warnerbros.com/', 1, 1, '2014-11-26 13:01:34', '2014-11-26 13:01:34'),
(137, 'movie', 'drama;romance', 'Titanic', 'Титаник', 'titanic-1997', '201411', 'e5e42eaf4d6542d232ee6414103f13a6656f5ad0.jpg', 1997, 0000, 'A seventeen-year-old aristocrat, expecting to be married to a rich claimant by her mother, falls in love with a kind but poor artist aboard the luxurious, ill-fated R.M.S. Titanic.', '84 years later, a 101-year-old woman named Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story to her granddaughter Lizzy Calvert, Brock Lovett, Lewis Bodine, Bobby Buell and Anatoly Mikailavich on the Keldysh about her life set in April 10th 1912, on a ship called Titanic when young Rose boards the departing ship with the upper-class passengers and her mother, Ruth DeWitt Bukater, and her fiancé, Caledon Hockley. Meanwhile, a drifter and artist named Jack Dawson and his best friend Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets to the ship in a game. And she explains the whole story from departure until the death of Titanic on its first and last voyage April 15th, 1912 at 2:20 in the morning.', 'Тансаг зэрэглэлийн Титаник хөлөг онгоцоор аялалд гарсан 17 настай язгууртан бүсгүй эелдэг, сайхан сэтгэлтэй зураач залууд дурлана. Гэвч бүсгүйг ээж нь чинээлэг хөрөнгөтөнтэй суулгахаар тохиролцсон байна.', '84 жилийн дараа 101 настай Роза өөрийн түүхийг ач охиндоо ярьж өгнө. 1912 оны 4 сарын 10-нд далайд гарсан тансаг зэрэглэлийн Титаник хөлөг мөсөн уул мөргөж 4-р сарын 15-нд сүйрэх хүртэл хөлөг онгоц дээр өрнөсөн үйл явдлыг нэг бүрчлэн хүүрнэнэ.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zCy5WQ9S4c0', '', 194, 3, 'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation, Paramount Pictures', 'James Cameron', 'James Cameron', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/TitanicMovie', 'http://www.titanicmovie.com/', '1997-12-19', 'Leonardo DiCaprio, Kate Winslet', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.titanicmovie.com/', 1, 1, '2014-11-26 13:14:29', '2014-11-26 13:14:29'),
(138, 'movie', 'adventure;biography;drama', 'Lawrence of Arabia', 'Арабын Лоуринс', 'lawrence-of-arabia-1962', '201411', '9e171d673b22439361006bfa0a0f48120adbb8b5.jpg', 1962, 0000, 'A flamboyant and controversial British military figure and his conflicted loyalties during his World War I service in the Middle East.', 'After a prologue showing us Lawrence''s ultimate fate, we flash back to Cairo in 1917. A bored general staffer, Lawrence talks his way into a transfer to Arabia. Once in the desert, he befriends Sherif Ali Ben El Kharish (Omar Sharif, making one of the most spectacular entrances in movie history) and draws up plans to aid the Arabs in their rebellion against the Turks. No one is ever able to discern Lawrence''s motives in this matter: Prince Feisal (Alec Guinness) dismisses him as yet another "desert-loving Englishman," and his British superiors assume that he''s either arrogant or mad. Using a combination of diplomacy and bribery, Lawrence unites the rival Arab factions of Feisal and Auda Abu Tayi (Anthony Quinn). After successfully completing his mission, Lawrence becomes an unwitting pawn of the Allies, as represented by Gen. Allenby (Jack Hawkins) and Dryden (Claude Rains), who decide to keep using Lawrence to secure Arab cooperation against the Imperial Powers. While on a spying mission to Deraa, Lawrence is captured and tortured by a sadistic Turkish Bey (Jose Ferrer). In the heat of the next battle, a wild-eyed Lawrence screams "No prisoners!" and fights more ruthlessly than ever. Screenwriters Robert Bolt and Michael Wilson used T. E. Lawrence''s own self-published memoir The Seven Pillars of Wisdom as their principal source, although some of the characters are composites, and many of the "historical" incidents are of unconfirmed origin. Two years in the making (you can see O''Toole''s weight fluctuate from scene to scene), the movie, lensed in Spain and Jordan, ended up costing a then-staggering $13 million and won seven Academy Awards, including Best Picture and Best Director. The 1962 Royal Premiere in London was virtually the last time that David Lean''s director''s cut was seen: 20 minutes were edited from the film''s general release, and 15 more from the 1971 reissue. This abbreviated version was all that was available for public exhibition until a massive 1989 restoration, at 216 minutes that returned several of Lean''s favorite scenes while removing others with which he had never been satisfied. ~ Hal Erickson, Rovi', 'Томас Эдвард Лоуринс - баатар, луйварчин, алуурчин, эр зоригтон. Тэр Арабын цөлд мандаж явсан эрэлхэг дайчин. Дэлхийн 1-р дайнд тэрээр Британийн армид үнэнчээр зүтгэж, дайны явцыг өөрийнхөө аргаар эргүүлнэ.', '46 насандаа Дорсэтэд өөд болсон Лоуринсийн амьдралыг 1916 оны Кайро хотоос ухраан үзүүлнэ. Дэлхийн 1-р Дайнд Туркийн эсрэг боссон Арабын хувьсгалын явцыг судлах үүрэгтэй Лоуринс эхлээд цөөн хүнтэй партизануудыг толгойлно. Удалгүй өөрийн гэсэн армитай болж, Туркуудын эсрэг дээрэм тонуул, галт тэрэг дэлбэлэх үйл ажиллагааг зохион байгуулдаг. Хоёр жилийн дараа цэргүүдээ удирдан Английн Генералд Оттоманы эзэнт гүрнийг түлхэн унагаахад нь тусалдаг.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zmr1iSG3RTA', '', 216, 6, 'Horizon Pictures', 'David Lean', 'T.E. Lawrence, Robert Bolt', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/LawrenceofArabia', 'https://www.facebook.com/LawrenceofArabia', '1998-12-10', 'Peter O''Toole, Alec Guinness, Anthony Quinn', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/LawrenceofArabia', 1, 1, '2014-11-26 13:39:26', '2014-11-26 13:39:26'),
(139, 'movie', 'horror;mystery;thriller', 'Psycho', 'Галзуу хүн', 'psycho-1960', '201411', '6b060f0039a8eb1ac099296cf17f72014a9f20ba.jpg', 1960, 0000, 'Norman Bates, whose "old dark house" and adjoining motel are not the place to spend a quiet evening. No one knows that better than Marion Crane (Janet Leigh), the film''s ill-fated heroine who is victimized in the now-notorious "shower scene."', 'Phoenix officeworker Marion Crane is fed up with the way life has treated her. She has to meet her lover Sam in lunch breaks and they cannot get married because Sam has to give most of his money away in alimony. One Friday Marion is trusted to bank $40,000 by her employer. Seeing the opportunity to take the money and start a new life, Marion leaves town and heads towards Sam''s California store. Tired after the long drive and caught in a storm, she gets off the main highway and pulls into The Bates Motel. The motel is managed by a quiet young man called Norman who seems to be dominated by his mother.', 'Норман Бэйтсийн хуучин дэн буудал сэтгэл амар хоног төөрүүлэх газар биш. Гэвч үүнийг хөөрхий бүсгүй хэрхэн мэдэх билээ.', 'Нарийн бичиг бүсгүй Марион Крэйн амьдралаа өөрчлөхийг хүсдэг. Дурлалт залуу Сэм нь мөнгөний асуудлаас болоод өөртэй нь гэрлэж чадахгүй. Нэгэн Баасан гаригт Марионы дарга 40000 долларыг банканд хийлгэхээр явуулна. Марион мөнгийг авч, хотоос гарч зугтаана. 36 цаг унтаагүй тул замдаа даруухан дэн буудалд хоног төөрүүлэхээр болдог. Буудлын эзэн залуу ээжийнхээ үгнээс гардаггүй хүн шиг харагдана.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ps8H3rg5GfM', '', 109, 18, 'Shamley Productions', 'Alfred Hitchcock', 'Robert Bloch, Joseph Stefano', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/AlfredHitchcockandtheMakingofPsycho', 'http://www.thepsychomovies.com/films/psycho/', '1999-09-08', 'Anthony Perkins, Janet Leigh, Vera Miles', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.thepsychomovies.com/films/psycho/', 1, 1, '2014-11-26 13:56:28', '2014-11-26 13:56:28'),
(140, 'movie', 'drama', 'Sunset Boulevard', 'Нарлаг Гудамж', 'sunset-boulevard-1950', '201411', '7fed24aef25c68e5bd6537de7ce8cfbb5e9cefab.jpg', 1950, 0000, 'The story, set in ''50s Hollywood, focuses on Norma Desmond, a silent-screen goddess whose pathetic belief in her own indestructibility has turned her into a demented recluse. The crumbling Sunset Boulevard mansion where she lives with only her butler, Max who was once her director and husband has become her self-contained world. Norma dreams of a comeback to pictures and she begins a relationship with Joe Gillis, a small-time writer who becomes her lover, that will soon end with murder and total madness', 'The story, set in ''50s Hollywood, focuses on Norma Desmond, a silent-screen goddess whose pathetic belief in her own indestructibility has turned her into a demented recluse. The crumbling Sunset Boulevard mansion where she lives with only her butler, Max who was once her director and husband has become her self-contained world. Norma dreams of a comeback to pictures and she begins a relationship with Joe Gillis, a small-time writer who becomes her lover, that will soon end with murder and total madness', '1950-иад оны Холливуд. Залуудаа гялалзаж явсан супер од Норма Десмонд одоо хөгширч, мартагдсан нэгэн. Гэвч тэр шинэ амьдралаа хүлээн зөвшөөрөхөөс татгалзаж, Нарлаг Гудамжны байшиндаа өөрийгөө Холливудын од хэвээрээ хэмээн төсөөлөн суудаг.', 'Гэрийн үйлчлэгч Макс нь залуудаа кино найруулагч, Нормагийн нөхөр байсан бол одоо Нормагийн хуучин амьдралыг сануулах цорын ганц хүн нь болсон. Гэтэл Норма хөлсний зохиолчтой учирч, өөртөө зориулан кино бичүүлэхээр болно. Харамсалтай нь түүний мөрөөдөл хүн амины хэргээр төгсдөг.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y3P0Zpe-2og', '', 110, 18, 'Paramount Pictures', 'Billy Wilder', 'Charles Brackett, Billy Wilder', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/SunsetBlvdMovie', 'http://www.paramount.com/movies/sunset-boulevard', '1999-08-25', 'William Holden, Gloria Swanson, Erich von Stroheim', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.paramount.com/movies/sunset-boulevard', 1, 1, '2014-11-26 14:15:21', '2014-11-26 14:15:21'),
(141, 'movie', 'biography;comedy;crime', 'The Wolf of Wall Street', 'Волстрийтийн Чоно', 'the-wolf-of-wall-street-2013', '201411', 'dd45b2d12d727d36db0b9c90c186f760cf91c7c4.jpg', 2013, 0000, 'Martin Scorsese directs the story of New York stockbroker Jordan Belfort. From the American dream to corporate greed, Belfort goes from penny stocks and righteousness to IPOs and a life of corruption in the late 80s. Excess success and affluence in his early twenties as founder of the brokerage firm Stratton Oakmont warranted Belfort the title "The Wolf of Wall Street."', 'In The Wolf of Wall Street DiCaprio plays Belfort, a Long Island penny stockbroker who served 36 months in prison for defrauding investors in a massive 1990s securities scam that involved widespread corruption on Wall Street and in the corporate banking world, including shoe designer Steve Madden.', 'Жордан Белфортын бодит түүхээс сэдэвлэсэн кино. Том бизнесийн эзэн болох Америк мөрөөдлийн бодит биелэл. Белфорт сохор зоосгүй нэгэн хөрөнгийн зах зээл дээр шинэ компани танилцуулж IPO хийх аргаар асар богино хугацаанд хөрөнгийн зах зээлийн хамгийн том корпорацийг байгуулж чадсан тул түүнийг "Волстрийтийн Чоно" хэмээн нэрлэх болжээ.', 'Гүйлгээ ухаантай залуу баян чинээлэг брокер болтлоо дэвшиж, үнэ цэнэтэй бүхнийг үзсэнийхээ дараа гэмт хэрэг, хээл хахууль, засгийн газрыг хуурсан хэргээр шоронд сууна.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/iszwuX1AK6A" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0993846" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0993846/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Wolf of Wall Street (2013) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 180, 6, 'Paramount Pictures, Red Granite Pictures, Appian Way See', 'Martin Scorsese', 'Terence Winter (screenplay), Jordan Belfort (book)', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/TheWolfOfWallStreet', 'http://www.thewolfofwallstreet.com/index_splash.php', '2013-12-25', 'Leonardo DiCaprio, Jonah Hill, Margot Robbie', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.thewolfofwallstreet.com/index_splash.php', 1, 1, '2014-11-27 00:23:08', '2014-11-27 00:23:08'),
(142, 'movie', 'mystery;thriller', 'Shutter Island', 'Нууцлаг Арал', 'shutter-island-2010', '201411', 'fcecc66522840caae32f55c681e6e3008cdf6cd1.jpg', 2010, 0000, 'In 1954, U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels is investigating the disappearance of a murderess who escaped from a hospital for the criminally insane and is presumed to be hiding near-by.', 'He''s been pushing for an assignment on the island for personal reasons, but before long he wonders whether he hasn''t been brought there as part of a twisted plot by hospital doctors whose radical treatments range from unethical to illegal to downright sinister. Teddy''s shrewd investigating skills soon provide a promising lead, but the hospital refuses him access to records he suspects would break the case wide open. As a hurricane cuts off communication with the mainland, more dangerous criminals "escape" in the confusion, and the puzzling, improbable clues multiply, Teddy begins to doubt everything - his memory, his partner, even his own sanity', '1954 он. Холбооны мөрдөх товчооны маршал Тэдди Даниель сэтгэл мэдрэлийн эмнэлгээс оргосон галзуу гэмт хэрэгтэн эмэгтэйг илрүүлэх ажлаар Нууц Арал руу явна. Мөрдлөгийн явцад Тэдди эмэгтэйн алга болсон хэрэг өөр нэгэн хэргийг далдалж байгааг илрүүлнэ.', 'Тэдди Маршал хувийн шалтгаанаар Нууцлаг арлын эмнэлгийг эртнээс хараандаа авсан байжээ. Тиймээс эмнэлэгт ирсэн даруйдаа эмч нарын ёсзүйгүй, хууль бус ажиллагааг илрүүлэхээр ханцуй шамлан орно. Удалгүй хэргийн явцад ахиц гарсан ч эмнэлгийн талаас мөрдлөгийг зогсоохыг шаардана. Гэтэл далайн хар салхи дэгдэж, эмнэлгийн хараа хяналт сулрах үед Тэдди хамгийн аюултай өвчтнүүдийн хэсэгт очдог. Гэвч хэрэг явдал улам л төвөгтэй болох бөгөөд Тэдди өөрийн эрүүл ухаандаа ч эргэлзэхэд хүрнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/5iaYLCiq5RM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt1130884" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1130884/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Shutter Island (2010) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 138, 18, 'Paramount Pictures', 'Martin Scorsese', 'Laeta Kalogridis (screenplay), Dennis Lehane (novel)', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/ShutterIsland', 'http://www.shutterisland.com/intl/fr/main/#/home', '2010-02-19', 'Leonardo DiCaprio, Emily Mortimer, Mark Ruffalo', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-27 00:33:26', '2014-11-27 00:33:26'),
(143, 'movie', 'action;drama;thriller', 'V for Vendetta', 'Цусан өшөө авагч В', 'v-for-vendetta-2005', '201411', 'ba6c48a7d51b47c5a9f14981199c4fc32b2cceed.jpg', 2005, 0000, 'The futuristic tale unfolds in a Great Britain that''s a fascist state. A freedom fighter known as V uses terrorist tactics to fight the oppressive society. He rescues a young woman from the secret police, and she becomes his unlikely ally', 'V for Vendetta takes place in an alternate vision of Britain in which a corrupt and abusive totalitarian government has risen to complete power. During a threatening run in with the secret police, an unassuming young woman named Evey (Natalie Portman) is rescued by a vigilante named V (Hugo Weaving) -- a caped figure both articulate and skilled in combat. V embodies the principles of rebellion from an authoritarian state, donning a mask of vilified would-be terrorist of British history Guy Fawkes and leading a revolution sparked by assassination and destruction. Evey becomes his unlikely ally, newly aware of the cruelty of her own society and her role in it. ~ Cammila Albertson, Rovi', 'Ирээдүйн Британи улсад фашист дэглэм тогтжээ. Эрх чөлөөний төлөө тэмцэгч В террористуудын тактикийг ашиглаж, бурангуй засаглалын эсрэг тэмцэнэ. Энэ зуурт нууц цагдан сэргийлэх газраас залуу бүсгүйг аварч, улмаар тэд хамтрагчид болдог.', 'Нууц цагдан сэргийлэхээс оргосон залуу бүсгүй Эвиег В нэрт дээрэмчин аварна. Хоёулаа л тулааны эрдэмд гаргууд тул Британийн түүхэнд бичигдэн үлдсэн террорист Гай Фовксийн дүрийг ашиглан харгис засаглалын эсрэг тэмцэхээр баг бүрдүүлнэ. Энэ зуурт Эвие засаглалын буруу зарчмыг, өөрөө тэнд ямар үүрэг гүйцэтгэж явснаа ухаардаг.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/k_13fFIrhPk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0434409" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0434409/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="V for Vendetta (2005) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 132, 13, 'Jackmanou Pictures,Warnerbros pictures', 'James McTeigue', 'Andy Wachowski (screenplay), Lana Wachowski', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/VforVendettaFilm', 'http://wwws.warnerbros.fr/vforvendetta/', '2006-03-17', 'Hugo Weaving, Natalie Portman, Rupert Graves', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-27 01:14:35', '2014-11-27 01:14:35'),
(144, 'movie', 'action;drama', 'Gladiator', 'Гладиатор', 'gladiator-2000', '201411', '63eb4780866036a2edda4de22dbf4ef46485e9d1.jpg', 2000, 0000, 'When a Roman general is betrayed and his family murdered by an emperor''s corrupt son, he comes to Rome as a gladiator to seek revenge.', 'Maximus is a powerful Roman general, loved by the people and the aging Emperor, Marcus Aurelius. Before his death, the Emperor chooses Maximus to be his heir over his own son, Commodus, and a power struggle leaves Maximus and his family condemned to death. The powerful general is unable to save his family, and his loss of will allows him to get captured and put into the Gladiator games until he dies. The only desire that fuels him now is the chance to rise to the top so that he will be able to look into the eyes of the man who will feel his revenge', 'Ромын эзэнт гүрний генерал эзэн хааны өв залгамжлагчийн санаархалд гэр бүлээ алдаж, боол болон худалдагдана. Ингээд өшөөгөө авахаар Гладиатор болж Ромд эргэн ирдэг.', 'Максимус бол Ромын хамгийн чадалтай генералуудын нэг. Түүнийг Ромын ард түмэн, нас өндөр болсон эзэн хаан хайрлаж, хүндэлдэг. Тиймээс эзэн хаан өөд болохдоо төрсөн хүү Коммодусыг үл тоон Максимусыг өөрийн өв залгамжлагчаар зарлана. Хаан ширээний төлөөх тэмцэлд Максимус ялагдаж, гэр бүлээ алдаж, боолын худалдаачдын гарт орно. Гэвч хайртай гэр бүлийнхээ өшөө авахын тулд Гладиатор болон эргэн ирдэг.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/W1rNFuKFTnc" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0172495" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0172495/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Gladiator (2000) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 155, 16, 'Universal pictures,Dreamworks', 'Ridley Scott', 'David Franzoni (story), David Franzoni', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/gladiatormovie', 'http://www.dreamworks.com/gladiator/', '2000-05-05', 'Russell Crowe, Joaquin Phoenix, Connie Nielsen', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'http://www.dreamworks.com/gladiator/', 1, 1, '2014-11-27 01:48:45', '2014-11-27 01:48:45'),
(145, 'movie', 'crime;drama;fantasy', 'The Green Mile', 'Ногоон бүс', 'the-green-mile-1999', '201411', '6b7806e074640d700e3adc6726be16166f57a917.jpg', 1999, 0000, 'The lives of guards on Death Row are affected by one of their charges: a black man accused of child murder and rape, yet who has a mysterious gift.', 'In 1935, inmates at the Cold Mountain Correctional Facility call Death Row "The Green Mile" because of the dark green linoleum that tiles the floor. Paul Edgecomb (Tom Hanks) is the head guard on the Green Mile when a new inmate is brought into his custody: John Coffey (Michael Clarke Duncan), convicted of the sadistic murder of two young girls. Despite his size and the fearsome crimes for which he''s serving time, Coffey seems to be a kind and well-mannered person who behaves more like an innocent child than a hardened criminal. Soon Edgecomb and two of his fellow guards, Howell (David Morse) and Stanton Barry Pepper), notice something odd about Coffey: he''s able to perform what seem to be miracles of healing among his fellow inmates, leading them to wonder just what sort of person he could be, and if he could have committed the crimes with which he was charged. The Green Mile also stars James Cromwell as the warden; Michael Jeter, Sam Rockwell, and Graham Greene as inmates awaiting dates with the electric chair; and Harry Dean Stanton as a clever trustee. ~ Mark Deming, Rovi', 'Ялын тогтоол гүйцэтгэгч хуягууд шинэ хоригдлыг хүлээн авсанаас хойш хачирхалтай хэрэг тохиолдож эхэлнэ. Хүүхэд хүчирхийлж, хороосон хэргээр ял сонссон том биетэй хар арьстан жирийн хүн биш, ер бусын авъяастай нэгэн байдаг.', '1935 он. Хүйтэн уулын ялын тогтоол гүйцэтгэх түр хорихын ахлах хуяг Пол Эджкомб хоёр бяцхан охины амийг хөнөөсөн хэрэгтнийг хүлээн авна. Гэтэл аварга том биетэй алуурчин эелдэг, зөөлөн хүн байж таарна. Удалгүй Пол болон шоронгийн хуягууд энэ том хүний өөр нэгэн авъяасыг олж мэддэг. Цахилгаан суудалд суух өдөр дөхөх тусам залуус хэрэгтнийг үнэхээр гэмт хэрэг үйлдсэн эсэхэд эргэлзэж эхэлнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/Ki4haFrqSrw" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0120689" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120689/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Green Mile (1999) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 189, 13, 'Warnerbros pictures,Castel rock entertaiment', 'Frank Darabont', 'Stephen King (novel), Frank Darabont', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/TheGreenMileOfficial', 'http://stephenking.com/library/novel/green_mile:_the_complete_serial_novel_the.html', '1999-12-10', 'Tom Hanks, Michael Clarke Duncan, David Morse', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-27 01:59:46', '2014-11-27 01:59:46'),
(146, 'movie', 'crime;drama', 'American History X', 'Америкийн нууц түүх', 'american-history-x-1998', '201411', '87f040547e8ce89abf74d8594b5b9e8568940173.jpg', 1998, 0000, 'A former neo-nazi skinhead tries to prevent his younger brother from going down the same wrong path that he did.', 'Teen Danny Vinyard (Edward Furlong) races to tell his older brother, neo-Nazi Derek (Edward Norton), about the young blacks breaking into his car in front of the house, whereupon Derek gets his gun and with no forethought shoots the youths in their tracks. Tried and convicted, Derek is sent away for three years in prison, where he acquires a different outlook as he contrasts white-power prisoners with black Lamont (Guy Torry), his prison laundry co-worker and eventual pal. Meanwhile, Danny, with a shaved head and a rebellious attitude, seems destined to follow in his big brother''s footsteps. After Danny writes a favorable review of Hitler''s Mein Kampf, black high-school principal Sweeney (Avery Brooks) puts Danny in his private "American History X" course and assigns him to do a paper about his older brother, who was a former student of Sweeney''s. This serves to introduce flashbacks, with the film backtracking to illustrate Danny''s account of Derek''s life prior to the night of the shooting. Monochrome sequences of Derek leading a Venice, California gang are intercut with color footage of the mature Derek ending his past neo-Nazi associations and attempting to detour Danny away from the group led by white supremacist, Cameron (Stacy Keach), who once influenced Derek.', 'Неонацист явсан залуу шоронгоос гарч, дүүгээ өөрийнх нь хийсэн алдааг давтахаас сэргийлэхийн тулд чадах бүхнээ хийнэ.', 'Неонацист үзэлтэй Дерек машинд нь зөвшөөрөлгүй халдсан харуудыг буудсанаар гурван жил хорих ял сонсоно. Гэвч шоронд тэрээр хар арьст Ламонттой нөхөрлөж, цагаан арьстнуудтай тэрсэлдэнэ. Энэ зуурт Дерекийн дүү Дэнни хар арьстнуудыг үзэн ядагчдын эгнээнд элсэж, ахынхаа хуучин багш Виниегийн шавь болдог. Бүхнийг ойлгосон Дерек дүүдээ неонацистуудын буруу үзлийг ухуулан тайлбарлахыг оролдоно.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/JsPW6Fj3BUI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0120586" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120586/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="American History X (1998) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 119, 18, 'New line cinema', 'Tony Kaye', 'David McKenna', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/americanhistoryxmovie', 'http://www.edward-norton.org/americanhx.html', '1998-11-20', 'Edward Norton, Edward Furlong, Beverly D''Angelo', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-11-27 02:14:17', '2014-11-27 02:14:17'),
(147, 'series', 'adventure;fantasy', 'The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring', 'Бөгжний Эзэн: Бөгжний Нөхөрлөл', 'the-lord-of-the-rings-the-fellowship-of-the-ring-2001', '201411', 'a1a69073fd562374d7d881fca07a9c5250303eba.jpg', 2001, 0000, 'Assisted by a Fellowship of heroes, Frodo Baggins plunges into a perilous trek to take the mystical One Ring to Mount Doom so that it and its magical powers can be destroyed and never possessed by evil Lord Sauron. The astonishing journey begins in the first film of director/co-writer Peter Jackson''s epic trilogy that redefined fantasy filmmaking. This imaginative foray into J.R.R. Tolkien''s Middle-earth won 4 Academy Awards (R)* and earned 13 total nominations including Best Picture.', 'An ancient Ring thought lost for centuries has been found, and through a strange twist in fate has been given to a small Hobbit named Frodo. When Gandalf discovers the Ring is in fact the One Ring of the Dark Lord Sauron, Frodo must make an epic quest to the Cracks of Doom in order to destroy it! However he does not go alone. He is joined by Gandalf, Legolas the elf, Gimli the Dwarf, Aragorn, Boromir and his three Hobbit friends Merry, Pippin and Samwise. Through mountains, snow, darkness, forests, rivers and plains, facing evil and danger at every corner the Fellowship of the Ring must go. Their quest to destroy the One Ring is the only hope for the end of the Dark Lords reign', 'Фродо нэрт одой хэсэг нөхдийн хамт Мөхлийн уулнаа нууцлаг нэгэн бөгжийг аваачиж устгахаар адал явдлаар дүүрэн аялалд мордоно. Хамгийн гол нь манай баатрууд харанхуйн шидтэнээс урьтах ёстой.', 'Фродо нэрт бяцхан одой зуу зуун жилийн турш алга болсон хэмээн ам дамжсан хар шидийн нэгэн бөгжийг олжээ. Гандалф бөгжийг үзээд харын хүчний хамгийн хүчирхэг шидтэн Сауроных гэдгийг мэдсэн тул Үхлийн уулнаа очиж, бөгжийг утсгах даалгавар өгнө. Энэ хариуцлагатай даалгаврыг биелүүлэхээр Гандалф, Леголас элф, Гимли одой, Арагорн, Боромир, Мэрри, Пипн, Сэмвайс нар Фродойн хамт аялалд гарна. Уулыг давж, усыг гатлан, цас мөсийг туулж, харанхуй ой, хар хүчнийхэнтэй тэмцэн харын шидтэний ноёлолыг устгах аялал адал явдлаар дүүрэн өрнөнө.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/V75dMMIW2B4" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0120737" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120737/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring (2001) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 178, 13, 'New Line Cinema', 'Peter Jackson', 'J.R.R. Tolkien, Fran Walsh', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Lord-of-the-Rings-The-Fellowship-of-the-Ring/280234464001', 'http://www.lordoftherings.net/', '2001-12-19', 'Elijah Wood, Ian McKellen, Orlando Bloom', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.lordoftherings.net/', 2, 2, '2014-11-27 02:25:57', '2014-12-12 13:00:20'),
(148, 'series', 'adventure;fantasy', 'The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King', 'Бөгжний Эзэн: Эзэн хаан эргэн ирсэн нь', 'the-lord-of-the-rings-the-return-of-the-king-2003', '201411', '7070009849e8a158ee30ff412f864fdaba972ee4.jpg', 2003, 0000, 'The final battle for Middle-earth begins. Frodo and Sam, led by Gollum, continue their dangerous mission toward the fires of Mount Doom in order to destroy the One Ring.', 'While Frodo & Sam continue to approach Mount Doom to destroy the One Ring, unaware of the path Gollum is leading them, the former Fellowship aid Rohan & Gondor in a great battle in the Pelennor Fields, Minas Tirith and the Black Gates as Sauron wages his last war against Middle-Earth.', 'Дунд тивд эцсийн тулаан өрнөнө. Фродо, Сэм хоёр Голлумаар газарчлуулан Үхлийн уулны галд хүрэхээр аялалаа үргэлжлүүлнэ.', 'Фродо, Сэм хоёр Голлумын санаархлыг үл мэднэ. Энэ зуурт хуучин нөхөрлөлөөс Ронан, Гондор нар дунд тивийн дайныг удирдана. Саурон одоо эцсийн дайралтаа хийхээр төлөвлөж байна.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r5X-hFf6Bwo', '', 201, 3, 'New Line Cinema, WingNut Films', 'Peter Jackson', 'J.R.R. Tolkien, Fran Walsh', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/lordoftheringstrilogy', 'http://www.lordoftherings.net/', '2003-12-17', 'Elijah Wood, Viggo Mortensen, Ian McKellen', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.lordoftherings.net/', 2, 2, '2014-11-27 07:41:05', '2014-12-12 12:59:42');
