(202, 'movie', 'biography;drama;thriller', 'Captain Phillips', 'Ахмад Филипс', 'and-dangerous-days-at-sea-by', '201411', 'cf0368f559f56087599b043ee9d73560876461d8.jpg', 2013, 0000, 'The true story of Captain Richard Phillips and the 2009 hijacking by Somali pirates of the US-flagged MV Maersk Alabama, the first American cargo ship to be hijacked in two hundred years.', 'When a cargo freighter passes just outside Somalian waters, some men in a motorboat approaches the freighter and starts shooting at it. The Captain, Richard Phillips deduces they''re pirates so he tries to keep them off the ship but fails. They come on board so Phillips instructs the crew to hide. The pirates go to the bridge and tells Phillips they want money and when Phillips offers what they have which is about $30,000, the leader has his mind set on getting millions. He plans to take the crew hostage and hold them for ransom. But since they are hiding he goes off to find them. Eventually the crew captures the leader. His companions who have Phillips, demands they be allowed to go in the lifeboat. They let them but they keep Phillips. They try to go to Somalia but the U.S. Navy arrives and tries to stop them even if it means losing Phillips.', 'Өнгөрсөн 200 жилд далайн дээрэмчдийн гарт орсон цорын ганц хөлгийн ахмадад тохиолдсон бодит түүхээс сэдэвлэсэн кино.', 'Ачаа тээврийн онгоц Сомалийн эргийг өнгөрч явтал моторт завьтай зэвсэглэсэн дээрэмчид онгоцонд орж ирнэ. Ахмад Филипсийн зугтах оролдлого бүтэлгүйтэж, хөлөг онгоц далайн дээрэмчдийн гарт орох мөчид ахмад хөлгийн багийнхныг нууна. Хөлөг дээрх хүмүүсийг барьцаалж, Америкийн засгийн газраас мөнгө шаардах зорилготой байсан дээрэмчдийн төлөвлөгөө бүтэлгүйтсэнд бухимдаж, тэд Ахмадыг авч зугтана.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/_3ASoBrFGlc" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1535109" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1535109/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Captain Phillips (2013) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 134, 16, 'Columbia Pictures', 'Paul Greengrass', 'Billy Ray (screenplay), Richard Phillips (based upon the book "A Captain''s Duty: Somali Pirates, Navy SEALS, and Dangerous Days at Sea" by)', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/CaptainPhillipsMovie', 'http://www.captainphillipsmovie.com/site/', '2013-10-11', 'Tom Hanks, Barkhad Abdi, Barkhad Abdirahman', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-03 03:57:39', '2014-12-03 03:57:39'),
(203, 'movie', 'scifi;thriller', 'Gravity', 'Татах хүч', 'jon-s-cuar-n', '201411', 'fc1a7e88c1de6c690ab91f7d06c6fe903841761b.jpg', 2013, 0000, 'A medical engineer and an astronaut work together to survive after a catastrophe destroys their shuttle and leaves them adrift in orbit.', 'Dr. Ryan Stone (Sandra Bullock) is a brilliant medical engineer on her first shuttle mission, with veteran astronaut Matt Kowalsky (George Clooney) in command of his last flight before retiring. But on a seemingly routine spacewalk, disaster strikes. The shuttle is destroyed, leaving Stone and Kowalsky completely alone - tethered to nothing but each other and spiraling out into the blackness', 'Сансрын хөлөг нь сүйрэхэд анагаахын инженер, сансрын нисгэгч хоёр хязгааргүй уудам сансарт хаягдаж, амьд үлдэхийн төлөө тэмцэнэ.', 'Доктор Риан Стөүн бол авъяаслаг анагаахын инженер. Харин Мэт Ковалский бол тэтгэвэртээ гарах дөхсөн туршлагатай сансрын нисгэгч. Хамтдаа сансарт ниссэн хоёр сансрын хөлгийн гадна шалгалт хийж явтал осол гарч, сансрын хөлөг сүйддэг. Харанхуй огторгуйд тэд хоёулхнаа үлдэнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/OiTiKOy59o4" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1454468" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1454468/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Gravity (2013) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 91, 13, 'Warner Bros Pictures', 'Alfonso Cuarón', 'Alfonso Cuarón, Jonás Cuarón', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/gravitymovie', 'http://gravitymovie.warnerbros.com/', '2013-10-04', 'Sandra Bullock, George Clooney, Ed Harris', '', 0, 7, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-03 04:02:44', '2014-12-03 04:02:44'),
(204, 'movie', 'biography;drama', 'Dallas Buyers Club', 'Далласын Худалдан Авагчдын Клуб', 'melisa-wallack', '201411', 'c2eb02ab4ab69dcf5f614a07bcd51424ccd4045c.jpg', 2013, 0000, 'In 1985 Dallas, electrician and hustler Ron Woodroof works around the system to help AIDS patients get the medication they need after he is himself diagnosed with the disease.', 'Dallas 1985. Electrician and sometimes rodeo bull rider Ron Woodroof lives hard, which includes heavy smoking, drinking, drug use (primarily cocaine) and casual sex. He is racist and homophobic. While in the hospital on a work related injury, the doctors discover and inform him that he is HIV+, and that he will most-likely die within thirty days. Ron is initially in angry denial that he would have a disease that only "faggots" have, but upon quick reflection comes to the realization that the diagnosis is probably true. He begins to read whatever research is available about the disease, which at this time seems to be most effectively treated by the drug AZT. AZT, however, is only in the clinical trials stage within the US. Incredulous that he, as a dying man, cannot pay for any drug which may save or at least prolong his life, he goes searching for it by whatever means possible. It eventually leads him to Mexico and a "Dr." Vass, an American physician whose license was revoked in the US because of his AIDS related work against US regulations. Dr. Vass leads Ron to a cocktail of other drugs, some vitamins, he believes are more effective in treating the symptoms, since the virus, as Ron learns, will always be in the system of those who have been exposed to it. Ron begins to smuggle these drugs not approved by the FDA into the US, not only for his own use but for sale to other HIV+ persons. In this venture, he goes into an unlikely partnership with a HIV+ transgender woman named Rayon, who he met in the hospital and who has greater contact with AIDS patients through the gay community. As they try to work both above ground to get the meds to those that need them and underground to avoid detection by especially the FDA, Ron comes up with an idea to circumvent the fact of selling the drugs - which are not considered drugs yet since they are not FDA approved - directly to the HIV+ population, which then should should not be against the law. Richard Barkley and Dr. Sevard, the FDA''s lead man on the file and one of Ron''s doctors respectively, the latter who sees clinical trials as the only way to determine the efficacy of drugs despite the fact that Ron and others would have probably died already without these drugs, try to stop Ron and Rayon at every turn. Caught in the middle is Dr. Eve Saks, another of Ron''s doctors, who understands why policies are place, but who can sympathize with Ron, Rayon and others - all her patients, directly or indirectly - in their situation.', '1985 оны Даллас. ДОХ-өөр өвчилсөн гэдгээ мэдсэн Рон Вүдрүф ижил өвчтэй хүмүүст хэрэгтэй эмчилгээг нь хүргэхийн төлөө тэмцэнэ.', '1985 оны Даллас хот. Цахилгаанчин Рон Вүдрүф хэнэггүй нэгэн. Рон хааяа бух сургах тэмцээнд орж, тамхи их татаж, архи ууж, хар тамхи хэрэглэж, бэлгийн харьцаандаа цэнзүүр тавьдаггүй. Тэр бас өнгөт арьстнууд, ижил хүйстнүүдэд таатай ханддаггүй. Нэгэн өдөр ажил дээрээ хөнгөн гэмтэл авсан Рон эмнэлэгт очоод өөрийгөө ДОХ-оор өвчилж, нэг сарын настай болсон гэдгээ мэддэг. Эхэндээ Рон гаж донтнуудын өвчнөөр оношилсонд уурлаж, бухимдах ч удалгүй онош үнэн гэдгийг хүлээн зөвшөөрнө. Амьдрах хугацаагаа бага ч болов сунгахын тулд Рон хууль зөрчихөөс ч айхгүй.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/U8utPuIFVnU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0790636" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0790636/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Dallas Buyers Club (2013) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 117, 18, 'Focus Features', 'Jean-Marc Vallée', 'Craig Borten, Melisa Wallack', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/DallasBuyersClub', 'http://m.focusfeatures.com/dallas_buyers_club/', '2013-11-22', 'Matthew McConaughey, Jennifer Garner, Jared Leto', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-03 04:08:50', '2014-12-03 04:08:50'),
(205, 'movie', 'drama;romance;scifi', 'Her', 'Бүсгүй', 'spike-jonze', '201411', '14dc0bb85a5aa3e2b092a5a2e980d2a2adbf6372.jpg', 2013, 0000, 'A lonely writer develops an unlikely relationship with his newly purchased operating system that''s designed to meet his every need', 'Theodore is a lonely man in the final stages of his divorce. When he''s not working as a letter writer, his down time is spent playing video games and occasionally hanging out with friends. He decides to purchase the new OS1, which is advertised as the world''s first artificially intelligent operating system, "It''s not just an operating system, it''s a consciousness," the ad states. Theodore quickly finds himself drawn in with Samantha, the voice behind his OS1. As they start spending time together they grow closer and closer and eventually find themselves in love. Having fallen in love with his OS, Theodore finds himself dealing with feelings of both great joy and doubt. As an OS, Samantha has powerful intelligence that she uses to help Theodore in ways others hadn''t, but how does she help him deal with his inner conflict of being in love with an OS?', 'Ганцаардсан зохиолч хүний бүх хэрэгцээг хангах зорилготойгоор зохион бүтээж, худалдаанд гаргасан үйлдлийн системд дурлана.', 'Теодерийн гэрлэлт бүтэлгүйтэж, эхнэрээсээ салж байгаа. Завтай үедээ Теодер компьютерийн тоглоом тоглож, найз нөхөдтэйгээ гадуур гарах дуртай. Гэвч зарим үед маш их ганцаардах тул энэ ганцаардлаа даван туулахаар шинэ үйлдлийн систем худалдаж авдаг. Энэ үйлдлийн системийг "Ухамсарт хиймэл оюун ухаан" хэмээх бөгөөд хүний хэрэгцээг бүгдийг хангах зориулалттай. Гэтэл удалгүй Теодер үйлдлийн системийн дуу хоолой болсон Самантад татагдаж эхэлдэг. Тэд хамтдаа цаг хугацааг өнгөрөөсөөр Теодер бүсгүйд бүрмөсөн дурлана. Энэ дурлал түүнийг маш их аз жаргалтай болгох ч бас эргэлзээ төрүүлнэ. Саманта хүчирхэг системээ ашиглан өөр хэн ч өгч чадахгүй зүйлийг Теодерт өгдөг. Гэхдээ үйлдлийн системд дурласан дотоод сэтгэлийн хямралд нь хэрхэн тусалж чадах билээ?', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/8UP93m1rjI4" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1798709" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1798709/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Her (2013) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 126, 16, 'Annapurna Pictures', 'Spike Jonze', 'Spike Jonze', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/herthemovie', 'http://www.herthemovie.com/#/home', '2014-01-10', 'Joaquin Phoenix, Amy Adams, Scarlett Johansson', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-03 04:13:46', '2014-12-03 04:13:46'),
(206, 'movie', 'crime;drama;thriller', '21 Grams', '21 грамм', 'guillermo-arriaga', '201411', '319ed7ee667b129caaa680d0fc23256218314a42.jpg', 2003, 0000, 'A freak accident brings together a critically ill mathematician, a grieving mother, and a born-again ex-con.', 'This is the story of three well-meaning but flawed people: Paul Rivers, an ailing mathematician lovelessly married to an English émigré; Christina Peck, an upper-middle-class suburban housewife, happily married homemaker with two young daughters, with hiding a secret past; and Jack Jordan, an ex-convict who has found in his Christian faith the strength to life a law-abiding life and raise a family. They will be brought together by a terrible accident that will change their lives. By the final frame, none of them will be the same as they will learn harsh truths about love, faith, courage, desire and guilt, and how chance can change our worlds irretrievably, forever.', 'Өвчин туссан хүн, гашуудаж гунигласан эх, буруудаж засарсан гэмтэн гурвын амьдралын зам санаандгүй огтолцоно.', 'Сайхан сэтгэлтэй боловч амьдралдаа алдаж, бүдэрч явсан гурван хүний зам огтолцоно. Өвчинд нэрвэгдсэн математикч Пол Риверс цагаач бүсгүйтэй хувь заяагаа холбож, сайхан амьдарсан нэгэн. Хоёр хүүхдийн ээж, гэрсэг бүсгүй Кристинагийн гэрлэлт бас л зөв сонголт байсан. Гэвч бүсгүйд нэгэн нууц бий. Харин Жэк Жордан Христэд итгэх итгэлийнхээ хүчээр амьдралаа зөв замд залж, шоронгоос гарсан. Энэ гурван хүн аймшигт ослын улмаас тааралдаж, хайр дурлал, итгэл найдвар, эр зориг, хүсэл тэмүүлэл, гэм зэмийн талаарх хатуу үнэнд суралцаж, цаашдын амьдралаа бүрмөсөн өөрчилнө.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/rXcyLOSBBVg" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0315733" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0315733/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="21 Grams (2003) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 124, 16, 'Focus Features', 'Alejandro González Iñárritu', 'Guillermo Arriaga', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/21gramsofficial', 'http://www.21-grams.com/index.php', '2003-11-19', 'Sean Penn, Benicio Del Toro, Naomi Watts', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-03 04:21:15', '2014-12-03 04:21:15'),
(207, 'movie', 'comedy;drama;musical', 'High Fidelity', 'Чин үнэнч сэтгэл', 'd-v-devincentis', '201411', '59edbce74fce8b1c09aabf5f92bdba6fd673e3a7.jpg', 2000, 0000, 'Rob, a record store owner and compulsive list maker, recounts his top five breakups, including the one in progress.', 'High Fidelity follows the ''mid-life'' crisis of Rob, a thirty-something record-store owner who must face the undeniable facts - he''s growing up. In a hilarious homage to the music scene, Rob and the wacky, offbeat clerks that inhabit his store expound on the intricacies of life and song all the while trying to succeed in their adult relationships. Are they listening to pop music because they are miserable? Or are they miserable because they listen to pop music? This romantic comedy provides a whimsical glimpse into the male view of the affairs of the heart.', 'Хөгжмийн дэлгүүрийн эзэн амьдралд нь тохиосон таван азгүй дурлалын түүхийг өгүүлнэ.', 'Гуч гарч яваа Роб пянзны дэлгүүрийн эзэн. Түүний дэлгүүрээр хааяа зочлох этгээд байрын нэгэн бүсгүй хөгжим болоод амьдралын ялгааг тодруулахаар маргалдана. Хүмүүс гунигтай үедээ поп хөгжим сонсдог уу? Эсвэл поп хөгжим сонсдог хүмүүс угаасаа л гутранги байдаг уу? Роб гэх энэ залуугаас эрэгтэй хүний зүрх сэтгэлийн асуудалд хандах хандлагыг харуулна.', '<iframe width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/6P4dXJ_Tvns" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0146882" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0146882/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="High Fidelity (2000) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 113, 13, 'Touchstone Pictures', 'Stephen Frears', 'Nick Hornby (book), D.V. DeVincentis', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/high.fidelity.the.movie', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/High_Fidelity_%28film%29', '2000-03-31', 'John Cusack, Iben Hjejle, Todd Louiso', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-03 04:31:30', '2014-12-03 04:31:30'),
(208, 'movie', 'mystery;thriller', 'Blow Out', 'Шуугиант дуу', 'brian-de-palma', '201411', '80023eeaff2b8872bb1a53bbad47d0f34bf8e4d7.jpg', 1981, 0000, 'A movie sound recordist accidentally records the evidence that proves that a car accident was actually murder and consequently finds himself in danger.', 'This stylish Brian DePalma thriller plays off the theme of the unsuspecting witness who discovers a crime and is thereby put in grave danger, but with a novel twist. Jack is a sound recordist who works on grade-B horror movies. Late one evening, he is recording sounds for use in his movies when he hears something unexpected through his sound equipment and records it. Curiosity gets the better of him when the media become involved, and he begins to unravel the pieces of a nefarious conspiracy. As he struggles to survive against his shadowy enemies and expose the truth, he doesn''t know whom he can trust', 'Киноны хөгжим бичдэг нэгэн залуу машины ослоор далдалсан хүн амины хэргийн нотолгоог санамсаргүй хуурцагт буулгана. Гэтэл дууны цаана нуугдсан үл мэдэгдэх гэмт хэрэгтний хараанд өртөнө.', 'Жэк бол аймшгийн төрлийн киноны хөгжмөөр мэргэшсэн хүн. Нэгэн үдэш тэрээр кинондоо ашиглах дуу хураахаар гарсан залуу сонсох ёсгүй зүйлээ хуурцагт буулгаж авна. Сониуч зандаа хөтлөгдөж, цааш судалсаар гэмт хэргийн гэрч болсноо мэддэг. Шуугиант дууны цаана нуугдсан гэмт хэрэгтэн хэн ч байж болох тул залуу хэнд ч итгэх аргагүй.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/rDve1A5EAvk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0082085" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0082085/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Blow Out (1981) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 107, 16, 'Cinema 77, Geria Productions, Filmways Pictures', 'Brian De Palma', 'Brian De Palma', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Brian-De-Palmas-Blow-Out/141877505841066', 'http://store.intrada.com/s.nl/it.A/id.8967/.f', '1981-07-24', 'John Travolta, Nancy Allen, John Lithgow', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-03 04:43:07', '2014-12-03 04:43:07'),
(209, 'movie', 'drama;thriller;war', 'Lore', 'Лора', 'robin-mukherjee', '201411', 'd92bb17849e7ab4b6205d6ef09fb6093574d7894.jpg', 2012, 0000, 'As the Allies sweep across Germany, Lore leads her siblings on a journey that exposes them to the truth of their parents'' beliefs. An encounter with a mysterious refugee forces Lore to rely on a person she has always been taught to hate.', 'Left to fend for themselves after their SS officer father and mother, a staunch Nazi believer, are interred by the victorious Allies at the end of World War II, five German children undertake a harrowing journey that exposes them to the reality and consequences of their parents'' actions. Led by the eldest sibling, 14-year old Lore (striking newcomer Saskia Rosendahl), they set out on a harrowing journey across a devastated country to reach their grandmother in the north. After meeting the charismatic Thomas, a mysterious young refugee, Lore soon finds her world shattered by feelings of both hatred and desire as she must learn to trust the one person she has always been taught to hate in order to survive. Lush cinematography and an evocative, haunting mood infuse this unconventional take on the Holocaust legacy with unforgettable impact.', 'Холбоотнууд Германыг эзлэх үед Лора эгч дүүсийнхээ хамт эцэг эхийнхээ итгэдэг байсан үнэний эрэлд гарна. Учир битүүлэг дүрвэгчтэй таарсан нь үзэн ядах ёстой хэмээн сургасан хүндээ найдахад хүргэнэ.', 'Дэлхийн хоёрдугаар дайны төгсгөлд Холбоотнууд Нацистуудыг ялж эхэлнэ. Нацистуудын итгэл үнэмшилд чин сэтгэлээсээ автсан эцэг эх нь өөд болсны дараа таван Герман хүүхдүүд бодит байдал, эцэг эхийнхээ хийсэн үйлдлийн үр дагаврыг нүдээрээ харна. Тэдний хамгийн ахмад 14 настай Лора дүү нараа дагуулан хойд нутагт амьдардаг эмээгийндээ очихоор сүйрч нурсан улсаа хөндлөн гулд туулна. Амьд үлдэхийн тулд үзэн яд гэж заалгасан хүмүүстээ найдах болсон нь Лорагийн сэтгэлийг хоёрдуулна.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/_QC_iASFCiM" frame