(210, 'movie', 'drama', 'Barbara', 'Барбара', 'harun-farocki', '201411', 'd7ec4a08678b69945ed189427ebd452df86e1ac2.jpg', 2012, 0000, 'A doctor working in 1980s East Germany finds herself banished to a small country hospital.', 'In 1980s East Germany, Barbara is a Berlin doctor banished to a country medical clinic for applying for an exit visa. Deeply unhappy with her reassignment and fearful of her co-workers as possible Stasi informants, Barbara stays aloof, especially from the good natured clinic head, Andre. Instead, Barbara snatches moments with her lover as she secretly prepares to defect one day. Despite her plans, Barbara learns more about her life that puts her desires and the people around her in a new light. With her changing perspective, Barbara finds herself facing a painful moral dilemma that forces her to choose what she values', '1980-аад оны зүүн Германд амьдардаг нэгэн эмч бүсгүй алс нутагт цөлөгдөнө. Баруун Германд амьдардаг найз залуугийнхаа тусламжтай сэм дүрвэхээр төлөвлөж байсан бүсгүй хамт ажилладаг эмч Андред татагдаж эхэлнэ.', '1980-аад оны үеийн зүүн Германд амьдарч байсан эмч бүсгүй Барбара улсаас гарах виз хүссэнийхээ улмаас хөдөөгийн жижиг эмнэлэгт ажиллахаар цөлөгдөнө. Шинэ томилгоондоо дурамжхан байсан бүсгүй намын мэдээлэгч байж болзошгүй ажлынхнаасаа дайжиж, хөндий хүйтэн царайлна. Гэвч бас дураараа амьдрахыг хүссэн тул эргэлзэж явсаар эцэст нь хүндхэн сонголттой тулгарна.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/AuhkKlrgJrk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt2178941" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2178941/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Barbara (2012) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 105, 13, 'Adopt Films', 'Christian Petzold', 'Christian Petzold (screenplay), Harun Farocki', 0, 0, 'https://de-de.facebook.com/Barbara.Film', 'http://www.barbara-der-film.de/', '2012-03-08', 'Nina Hoss, Ronald Zehrfeld, Rainer Bock', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-04 02:06:10', '2014-12-04 02:06:10'),
(211, 'movie', 'drama;history;war', 'The Downfall of Berlin Anonyma', 'Берлиний Эмэгтэй', 'max-f-rberb-ck', '201411', 'd37694b5cac72c2ecdb46db95772b0e67a2baf12.jpg', 2008, 0000, 'A woman tries to survive the invasion of Berlin by the Soviet troops during the last days of World War II.', 'A nameless woman keeps a diary as the Russians invade Berlin in the spring of 1945. She is in her early 30s, a patriotic journalist with international credentials; her husband, Gerd, a writer, is an officer at the Russian front. She speaks Russian and, for a day or two after the invasion, keeps herself safe, but then the rapes begin. She resolves to control her fate and invites the attentions of a Russian major, Andreij Rybkin. He becomes her protector of sorts subject to pressures from his own fellow soldiers and officers. Dramas play out in the block of flats where she lives. Is she an amoral traitor? She asks, "How do we go on living?" And what of Gerd and her diary?', 'Дэлхийн 2-р дайны төгсгөл үед нэр нь үл мэдэгдэх нэгэн бүсгүй Берлинд халдсан Оросын дайралтаас амьд үлдэхээр тэмцэнэ.', '1945 онд Зөвлөлтийн цэргүүд Берлинд орж ирэх үеийн үйл явдлын талаар нэр нь үл мэдэгдэх нэгэн бүсгүй өдрийн тэмдэглэлдээ бичиж үлдээнэ. Бүсгүй эх оронч үзэлтэй, алсын хараатай сэтгүүлч хүн. Түүний нөхөр Герд зохиолч боловч тэр мөчид Оросын хил дээр тулаанд орж яваа. Бүсгүй Оросоор ярих тул халдлагын дараа хоёр өдөр аюулгүй байж чаддаг. Гэвч цаашдаа хүчирхийлэл, харгислалаас зугтааж чадахгүй. Ийнхүү хувь заяатайгаа эвлэрсэн бүсгүй Оросын хошууч Андрейгийн анхаарлыг татаж, улмаар түүний ивээлд багтдаг.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/M6Ill1r1TvA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1035730" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1035730/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Downfall of Berlin: Anonyma (2008) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 131, 16, 'Constantin Films', 'Max Färberböck', 'Anonyma (book), Max Färberböck', 0, 0, 'http://www.theguardian.com/film/2009/nov/26/anonyma-a-woman-in-berlin', 'http://www.wsws.org/en/articles/2008/11/anon-n25.html', '2008-10-23', 'Nina Hoss, Evgeniy Sidikhin, Irm Hermann', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-04 02:22:38', '2014-12-04 02:22:38'),
(212, 'movie', 'drama', 'Jerichow', 'Жэричов тосгон', 'christian-petzold', '201411', '0b086d0fb99dfdb23c817ff5c4b6c14f198f7801.jpg', 2008, 0000, 'The dishonorably discharged Afghanistan veteran Thomas returns to his home village of Jerichow. Ali, a local Turkish-German businessman, owner of a snack-bar chain, hires him as a driver', 'The dishonorably discharged Afghanistan veteran Thomas returns to his home village of Jerichow. Ali, a local Turkish-German businessman, owner of a snack-bar chain, hires him as a driver. That''s when Thomas meets Laura, his Turkish boss''s young and attractive wife. A classic love triangle is born, unfolding in desolate northeast Germany, where thick forests suddenly end on cliffs overlooking the Baltic Sea. Caught between guilt and freedom, between passion and reason, the protagonists have no hopes for fulfillment of their dreams.', 'Афканистаны дайнаас гутамшигтайгаар чөлөөлөгдсөн хал цэрэг Томас төрсөн Жэричов тосгондоо эргэн ирнэ. Турк-Германы эрлийз Али нэрт бизнесмэн түүнийг жолоочийн ажилд авна.', 'Гэтэл Томас Алигийн залуу, дур булаам эхнэр Лаурад татагдаж эхэлнэ. Ийнхүү сонгодог хайрын гурвалжин үүснэ. Гэмших сэтгэл, эрх чөлөөтэй байх хүслийнхээ дунд хавчуулагдаж, яахаа мэдэхээ байсан гол дүрүүд маань мөрөөдлөө биелүүлэх найдвараа алдаж эхэлдэг.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/VlgHdr2-SBM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1224153" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1224153/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Jerichow (2008) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 93, 16, 'ARTE, Bayerischer Rundfunk (BR), Schramm Film Koerner & Weber', 'Christian Petzold', 'Christian Petzold', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Jerichow/59814697548', 'http://www.jerichow-der-film.de/', '2009-01-08', 'Benno Fürmann, Nina Hoss, Hilmi Sözer', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-04 02:29:11', '2014-12-04 02:29:11'),
(213, 'movie', 'drama;romance;thriller', 'Yella', 'Элла', 'christian-petzold', '201411', 'a0372098e4f37c52f13c2ef678faae0dcf71843a.jpg', 2007, 0000, 'Yella is estranged from her possessive and violent husband; but he can''t quite bring himself to give her up. When their fraught interaction finally comes to dramatic conclusion, Yella''s life takes an odd shift.', 'Christian Petzold''s drama deals with a woman, who leaves her hometown for a promising job and a new life, but is haunted by the truths of the past. As her marriage to Ben broke and her professional career has no future in her native town in the Eastern part of Germany, Yella has decided to search for a job in the West. When she gets to know Philipp, a smart executive at a private equity company in Hanover, she becomes his assistant and gets involved into the world of ruthless and big business. Realizing her dreams could come true with Philipp''s help, she starts hearing voices and sounds from her past, which menace her new and better life', 'Сайхан ажил хийж, сайн явахыг хүссэн нэгэн бүсгүй төрсөн нутгаа орхин алсыг зорино. Гэвч түүний өнгөрсөн амьдрал тийм ч амар мартагдахгүй.', 'Хартай, харгис нөхрийн гараас арайхийн мултарсан Элла Баруун Герман руу гарч, тэндээ Филип нэрт нэгэн залуутай танилцана. Хановер хотын хувийн өмчит компанид гүйцэтгэх захирлын ажилтай энэ ухаалаг залуу бүсгүйг туслахаараа авч, бүсгүй бизнесийн ертөнцийн тулаанд татагдан орно. Филипийн тусламжтай мөрөөдөлдөө хүрч болохоо ойлгосон бүсгүй гэнэт л хуучин амьдралынхаа хар бараан дуу чимээг сонсох болсоноор шинэ, сайхан амьдралдаа сэв суулгаж эхэлдэг.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/S7iZUwm7tVQ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0806686" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0806686/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Yella (2007) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 89, 13, 'Schramm Film Koerner & Weber, Zweites Deutsches Fernsehen (ZDF),', 'Christian Petzold', 'Christian Petzold', 0, 0, 'http://www.yella-der-film.de/', 'http://www.yella-der-film.de/', '2008-05-16', 'Nina Hoss, Devid Striesow, Hinnerk Schönemann', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-04 02:41:22', '2014-12-04 02:41:22'),
(214, 'movie', 'crime', 'Gold', 'Алт', 'thomas-arslan', '201411', 'eb30a54c176df3c0c7b3fd4e6677aa8eb5b0b5bb.jpg', 2013, 0000, 'In the summer of 1898, a small group of German compatriots head into the hostile northern interior of British Columbia in search for gold at the height of the Klondike Gold Rush', 'During the Klondike Gold Rush of 1898, Emily Meyer joins a group of German immigrants who travel to the Far North in search of gold deposits. The seven apprentice gold-diggers, who have no real idea of what awaits them, leave the town of Ashcroft, the end of the railway line and set off for their long journey. As they sink into the wilderness of Canada''s wide-open paces, fatigue is felt. Worse, the maps become uncertain. As a result, doubt sets in and conflicts burst forth..', '1898 оны зун, Клондикийн Алтны доншуучдын үеийн оргил үед алт олох хүсэлтэй хэсэг залууд зэрлэг хойд нутгийн зүг хөдөлнө.', '1898 оны Клондикийн Алтны доншуучдын хөдөлгөөний үеэр Германы цагаач Мэер алт хайж, хойд нутгийг зорино. Алт олборлох талаар ямар ч мэдлэггүй долоон залуу Эшкрофт хотоос алс нутаг руу зориглон хөдөлнө. Гэвч Канадын зэрлэг нутагт тэд төөрч, ядарч, тэр дороо л хагаралдаж эхэлдэг.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/IFkataff7UI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt2338846" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2338846/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Gold (2013) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 101, 13, 'Schramm Film Koerner & Weber, Red Cedar Films, Bayerischer Rundfunk (BR)', 'Thomas Arslan', 'Thomas Arslan', 0, 0, 'http://www.mgm.com/?', 'http://www.mgm.com/?', '2013-08-15', 'Nina Hoss, Marko Mandic, Peter Kurth', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 1, 1, '2014-12-04 02:49:46', '2014-12-04 02:49:46'),
(215, 'series', 'action;crime;drama', 'The Fast and the Furious Tokyo Drift', 'Галзуу хурд: Токио дрифт', 'the-fast-and-the-furious-tokyo-drift-2006', '201411', 'aa2e9936c285b57534a3bd65cb35bb6d73b32c2c.jpg', 2006, 0000, 'Alabama teenager Sean Boswell becomes a major competitor in the world of drift racing after moving in with his father in Tokyo to avoid a jail sentence in America.', 'After totaling his car in an illegal street race, Shaun Boswell is sent to live with his father, who is in the military, in Tokyo, Japan, to avoid juvy or even jail. While in school, he befriends Twinkie, a "military brat." Twinkie introduces him to the world of racing in Japan. Though forbidden to drive, he decides to race against D.K., the "Drift King", who has ties to the Yakuza, and loses, totaling the car because of his lack of knowledge of drifting, racing that involves dangerous hair pin turns. To repay his debt, he enters the underground world of drift street racing. As he becomes better and better, he must finally prove his worth in that world by once again racing D.K.', 'Син Босвель хорих ялаас зугтаж, Токио хотод нүүж ирнэ. Ирсэн даруйдаа л тэрээр гудамжны тулаанд татагдан орж, өмнөхөөсөө л илүү аюултай уралдаанд аз туршина.', 'Токиод ирээд Син Твинкитэй нийлж эхэлнэ. Твинки түүнд Японы машины уралдааныг үзүүлнэ. Машин барих эрхгүй ч Син "Дрифтийн хаан"-тай тулахаар болж, эцэст нь дрифт хийх чадваргүйдээ ичгэвтэр байдлаар хожигддог. Ингээд машины өрөнд орсон тул дрифтийн уралдаанд улам гүн татагдан орно.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/p8HQ2JLlc4E" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0463985" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0463985/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift (2006) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(funct