(216, 'series', 'action;crime;thriller', 'The Fast and the Furious', 'Галзуу хурд', 'the-fast-and-the-furious-2001', '201411', '7e8d3bf4ef614262a2c0bc553d096ade4d59c70c.jpg', 2001, 0000, 'Los Angeles police officer Brian O''Connor must decide where his loyalties really lie when he becomes enamored with the street racing world he has been sent undercover to destroy', 'Los Angeles street racer Dominic Toretto falls under the suspicion of the LAPD as a string of high-speed electronics truck robberies rocks the area. Brian O''Connor, an officer of the LAPD, joins the ranks of Toretto''s highly skilled racing crew undercover to convict Toretto. However, O''Connor finds himself both enamored with this new world and in love with Toretto''s sister, Mia. As a rival racing crew gains strength, O''Connor must decide where his loyalties really lie.', 'Гудамжны тулааныхан дунд зүсээ хувирган орж, тэдний талаар мэдээлэх үүрэгтэй цагдаа Бриан галзуу мэт хурдлан давхих тэдний амьдралд татагдаж эхэлнэ.', 'Лос Анжелес хотод гарсан дээрмийн үйл ажиллагаанд гудамжны уралдааны хаан Доменик Торэттог сэрдэж эхэлнэ. Улмаар цагдаагийн офицер Бриан О.Коннер Торэттог тагнуулдахаар гудамжны тулааныхантай нэгдэнэ. Гэвч Бриан Торэттогийн дүү Миад дурлаж, галзуу мэт хурдлан давхих тэдний амьдралд татагдаж эхэлдэг. Ингээд Бриан аль талд нь үлдэхээ шийдэх ёстой болно.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/7h9aEswMvSM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0232500" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0232500/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Fast and the Furious (2001) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/