(217, 'series', 'action;crime', '2 Fast 2 Furious', 'Галзуу хурд 2', '2-fast-2-furious-2003', '201411', '64b9f66c27a4588c207dcf23145a171f4a34cf29.jpg', 2003, 0000, 'Brian O''Conner and childhood friend Roman Pearce are re-united by the FBI to bring down a Miami drug exporter in exchange for clear records.', 'Former cop Brian O''Conner who teams up with his ex-con pal Roman Pearce to transport a shipment of ''dirty'' money for shady Miami-based import-export dealer Carter Verone, while actually working with undercover agent Monica Fuentes to bring Verone down.', 'Бриан болон түүний багын найз Роман Пиерс нар Миамигийн хар тамхи наймаалагчдын дунд орж, гэмт хэрэгтнийг илрүүлэх ажилд томилогдоно.', 'Бриан хуучны анд Романтай хамтран хар тамхины импорт, экспортын бизнес эрхэлдэг Картер Вэронэгийн туслахаар ажилд орно. Гэвч үнэндээ тэд Вэронэг барьж, өөрсдийн хавтаст хэргээ цэвэрлэх зорилготой юм.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/F_VIM03DXWI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0322259" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0322259/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="2 Fast 2 Furious (2003) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 107, 13, 'Universal Pictures', 'John Singleton', 'Gary Scott Thompson (characters), Michael Brandt', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/FastandFurious', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2_Fast_2_Furious', '2003-06-06', 'Paul Walker, Tyrese Gibson, Cole Hauser', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-05 