(222, 'series', 'action;adventure;scifi', 'G.I. Joe The Rise of Cobra', 'Жи Ай Жови: Кобрачуудтай тэмцсэн нь', 'g-i-joe-the-rise-of-cobra-2009', '201411', 'b8430ad2fc63e345e2925db6e0fd124325f7fd24.jpg', 2009, 0000, 'An elite military unit comprised of special operatives known as G.I. Joe, operating out of The Pit, takes on an evil organization led by a notorious arms dealer.', 'Two soldiers stationed in Kazahkstan (Captain Duke Hauser and his partner "Ripcord") are ordered to transport special warheads created by MARS, an arms'' manufacturer controlled by James McCullen. When they are attacked by thieves (led by Anastasia DeCobray, with whom Duke has history), they are saved by a top secret, international special forces unit known as "G.I. Joe". The leader of G.I. Joe, General Abernathy (or Hawk) is on the trail of the thieves: an evil organization called "Cobra". While Duke and Ripcord train to join the Joes, McCullen ("Destro") is secretly working for Cobra and plotting to recapture his metal-eating "Nanomite" warheads. Duke and Ripcord (with help from Heavy Duty, Snake Eyes, and the rest of the Joes) must prove that they are Real American Heroes -- by stopping the launch of these warheads before Cobra uses them to take over the world.', '"Жи.Ай.Жови" нэрт элит зэрэглэлийн олон улсын цэргийн хүчний байгууллага зэвсгийн худалдаа эрхлэгч, террорист Кобрагийн эсрэг тэмцэнэ.', 'Казакстан улсын нутагт үүрэг даалгавар гүйцэтгэж буй хоёр цэргийг тусгай зориулалтын цэнэгт хошуу тээвэрлэх ажилд томилдог. Гэтэл тэдний замд дайснууд отолт хийж, цэнэгт хошууг хулгайлдаг. Аз болоход "Жи.Ай.Жови" нэрт олон улсын тусгай хүчнийхэн ирж, хоёр цэргийг аварна. Тэд Кобра гэх нууц байгууллагаас цэнэгт хошуу хулгайлах хэрэг зохион байгуулсныг илрүүлж, цэргүүдийг бэлтгэн "Жи.Ай.Жови"-д элсүүлнэ. Бэлтгэгдсэн цэргүүд Кобрагийн хорон санаатнууд цөмийн цэнэгт хошууг дэлхий дахины эсрэг ашиглахаас урьтан олж авах дараагийн даалгавраа авна.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/MaNs64k_2xw" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1046173" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1046173/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra (2009) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 118, 13, 'Paramount Pictures, Spyglass Entertainment, Hasbro', 'Stephen Sommers', 'Stuart Beattie, David Elliot', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/G-I-Joe-Rise-of-Cobra-Film-2009/63396314477?ref=mf', 'http://www.gijoemovie.com/', '2009-08-07', 'Dennis Quaid, Channing Tatum, Marlon Wayans', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-05 01:19:57', '2014-12-12 12:41:29'),
(223, 'series', 'action;adventure;fantasy', 'Fantastic Four', 'Гайхамшигт Дөрөв', 'fantastic-four-2005', '201411', 'c51229b8af5ed7729e5d38d8b4f310ee619ff616.jpg', 2005, 0000, 'A group of astronauts gain superpowers after a cosmic radiation exposure and must use them to oppose the plans of their enemy, Doctor Victor Von Doom', 'Reed Richards, a brilliant but timid and bankrupt scientist, is convinced that evolution can be triggered by clouds of cosmic energy, and has calculated that Earth is going to pass one of these clouds soon. Together with his friend and partner, the gruff yet gentle astronaut muscle-man Ben Grimm, Reed convinces his conceited MIT classmate Dr. Victor Von Doom, now CEO of his own enterprise, to allow him access to his privately-owned space station. Von Doom agrees in exchange for control over the experiment and a majority of the profits from whatever benefits it brings. He thus brings aboard Susan Storm, his shy, though assertive chief genetics researcher and a former lover of Reed''s with whom she had an acrimonious break-up, and her diametrically opposed brother Johnny, the maverick and hot-headed playboy pilot. The astronauts make it home intact; however, before long they begin to mutate, developing strange and amazing powers as a result of their exposure to the cloud! Reed is able to.', 'Сансарт ниссэн судлаачид сансрын радио идэвхит туяаны нөлөөгөөр супер хүчтэй болно. Эргэж ирээд өөрсдийн дайсан Доктор Виктор Вон Дүүмийн эсрэг хэрэглэдэг.', 'Рийд Ричардс авъяастай, ухаалаг эрдэмтэн боловс санхүүгийн тал дээр тооцоо муутай. Тэр нэгэн өдөр сансар огторгуйн эрчим хүчээр цэнэглэгдсэн үүлсийн нөлөөгөөр хувьсал явагддаг болохыг олж мэднэ. Нээлтээ баталгаажуулахын тулд эрх мэдэл, ирээдүйд олох ашгийг барьцаалан сансарт хөөрөх үүдийг нээнэ. Түүнтэй хамт Рийдийн хуучин найз бүсгүй Сюзен, ах Жонни, найз Бэн хамт ниснэ. Тэдний нислэг амжилттай болж, гэртээ эсэн мэнд иргэн ирсэний дараа гэнэт л хачирхалтай мутаци явагдаж эхэлнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/27dZ5mJBnBY" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0120667" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120667/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Fantastic Four (2005) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 106, 13, 'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation, Marvel Entertainment', 'Tim Story', 'Mark Frost, Michael France', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Fantastic-Four/6022173238', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fantastic_Four_%28film%29', '2005-07-08', 'Ioan Gruffudd, Michael Chiklis, Chris Evans', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-05 01:53:30', '2014-12-12 12:41:24'),
(224, 'series', 'action;fantasy;scifi', 'Fantastic 4  Rise of the Silver Surfer', 'Гайхамшигт Дөрөв: Мөнгөлөг Сюрфер', 'fantastic-4-rise-of-the-silver-surfer-2007', '201411', 'b8cb6147a89f98de9025cf0af45374ad04b4b7f0.jpg', 2007, 0000, 'The Fantastic Four learn that they aren''t the only super-powered beings in the universe when they square off against the powerful Silver Surfer and the planet-eating Galactus.', 'Everything seems to be going great for the Fantastic Four. Reed and Sue are finally getting married, and things couldn''t seem better. However, when the mysterious Silver Surfer crashes things, they learn that they will have to deal with an old foe, and the powerful planet eating galactus', 'Мөнгөлөг Сюрфер нэртэй хүчирхэг дайсан гарч ирэх үед Гайхамшигт Дөрөв өөрсдөөс нь гадна өөр супер хүчтэй биетүүд байдгийг ойлгодог.', 'Гайхамшигт Дөрөвийн хувьд бүх зүйл голдрилдоо оржээ. Рийд, Сю нар гэрлэж, бүгд л аз жаргалтай байлаа. Гэтэл Мөнгөлөг Сюрфер нэрт хүчирхэг дайсан гарч ирэхэд Гайхамшигт Дөрөв дахин нэг удаа хүчээ нэгтгэнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/ZN7PWE2dyAY" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0486576" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0486576/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Fantastic 4: Rise of the Silver Surfer (2007) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 92, 13, 'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation, Constantin Film Produktion, Marvel Studios', 'Tim Story', 'Don Payne (screenplay), Mark Frost', 0, 0