(226, 'series', 'action;adventure;scifi', 'The Incredible Hulk', 'Гайхамшигт Халк', 'the-incredible-hulk-2008', '201411', '6c5b4714a199801444f662f85d5227beb3642b07.jpg', 2008, 0000, 'Bruce Banner, a scientist on the run from the U.S. Government must find a cure for the monster he emerges whenever he loses his temper. However, Banner then must fight a soldier whom unleashes himself as a threat stronger than he.', 'Depicting the events after the Gamma Bomb. ''The Incredible Hulk'' tells the story of Dr Bruce Banner, who seeks a cure to his unique condition, which causes him to turn into a giant green monster under emotional stress. Whilst on the run from military which seeks his capture, Banner comes close to a cure. But all is lost when a new creature emerges; The Abomination.', 'АНУ-ын засгийн газраас зугтаж яваа эрдэмтэн Брюс Баннер уурлаж бухимдсан үедээ аймшигт мангас болон хувирдаг. Тэр өөрийнхөө энэ дутагдлыг эмчлэх арга хайна.', 'Гайхамшигт Халк Доктор Брюс Баннерийн түүхийг өгүүлнэ. Уурлаж, бухимдсан үедээ аварга биет аймшигт ногоон мангас болон хувирдаг Брюс өөрийгөө эмчлэх арга эрэлхийлнэ. Ийнхүү амжилт олохын даваан дээр өөр нэгэн аварга биет, харгис биетээс хүмүүсийг аврахын тулд эмчлэгдэх хүслээ золионд гаргана.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/xbqNb2PFKKA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0800080" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0800080/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Incredible Hulk (2008) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 112, 13, 'Universal Pictures, Marvel Enterprises, Marvel Studios', 'Louis Leterrier', 'Zak Penn (screenplay), Zak Penn', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/Hulk', 'http://bd-dvd.sonypictures.jp/hulk/', '2008-06-13', 'Edward Norton, Liv Tyler, Tim Roth', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-05 02:39:12', '2014-12-12 12:41:02'),
(227, 'series', 'musical', 'X-Men 2', 'Икс хүмүүс 2', 'x-men-2-2003', '201411', '053b46bb821efaef5b8dd2b09c182e0b593b2cdc.jpg', 2003, 0000, 'The X-Men band together to find a mutant assassin who has made an attempt on the President''s life, while the Mutant Academy is attacked by military forces.', 'Several months have passed since The X-Men defeated Magneto and imprisoned him in a seemingly impregnable plastic chamber. One day, a mutant by the name of Nightcrawler infiltrates the White House and attempts to assassinate the president, setting off a chain reaction of anti-mutant measures by the government. Meanwhile, Logan is trying to discover his past. As scientist named William Stryker discovers Professor X''s secret school and Cerebro, Magneto''s partner, Mystique, is planning to break her leader out of prison. But when Professor X''s school is attacked by Stryker''s forces, Logan, Rogue, Iceman and a few are lucky to escape. Those who remain meet in Boston, where they form an uneasy alliance with Magneto to stop Stryker and rescue Professor', 'Мутантуудын ирээдүйд заналхийлсэн нэгэн эрдэмтнийг зогсоохын тулд Икс хүмүүс Магнэтотой нэгдэнэ. Энэ зуурт мутантуудын эсрэг хөдөлгөөнийг зогсоох хүсэлтэй нэгэн мутант цагаан ордонд нэвтрэн ордог.', 'Икс хүмүүс Магнэтог ялж, засгийн газрын хуванцар шоронд хорьсон байна. Харин Магнэтогийн үнэнч найз Мистик түүнийг аврах төлөвлөгөө зохиодог. Энэ зуурт зүсээ хувиргагч нэгэн мутант Цагаан ордонд нэвтэрч, ерөнхийлөгчид мутантуудын эсрэг хөдөлгөөнийг зогсоох шаардлага тавьдаг. Харин Логан өөрийн өнгөрснөө олж мэдэх эрэл хайгуул хийсээр Виллиам Страйкерыг олж, энэ эрдэмтэн дэлхий дээрх бүх мутантуудыг устгах зорилготойг олж мэддэг. Страйкерийн эсрэг Икс хүмүүс Магнэтотой нэгдэнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/voxI4h7Jzmo" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0290334" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0290334/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="X-Men 2 (2003) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 134, 13, 'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation, Marvel Enterprises, Donners'' Company', 'Bryan Singer', 'Zak Penn (story), David Hayter', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/xmenmovies', 'http://marvel.com/movies/X-Men.X2~colon~_X-Men_United', '2003-05-02', 'Patrick Stewart, Hugh Jackman, Halle Berry', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-05 02:44:21', '2014-12-12 12:40:57'),
(228, 'series', 'action;adventure;scifi', 'The Wolverine', 'Нохой зээх', 'the-wolverine-2013', '201411', 'aa61f60ef7efa886efee7338708d882a83be58f9.jpg', 2013, 0000, 'When Wolverine is summoned to Japan by an old acquaintance, he is embroiled in a conflict that forces him to confront his own demons.', 'In modern day Japan, Wolverine is out of his depth in an unknown world as he faces his ultimate nemesis in a life-or-death battle that will leave him forever changed. Vulnerable for the first time and pushed to his physical and emotional limits, he confronts not only lethal samurai steel but also his inner struggle against his own immortality, emerging more powerful than we have ever seen him before', 'Японд уригдаж очсон Нохой зээх ээдрээтэй адал явдлыг туулах зууртаа дотоод сэтгэлийн зөрчилдөөнийг даван гарч, илүү хүчирхэг болно.', 'Хайртай бүсгүй Жэйнийг өөрийн гараар хөнөөсөндөө гутарч, гунигласан Нохой зээх үхсэнээс ялгаагүй амьдрана. Гэтэл хуучны танил нь түүнийг Японд авчирч, охиныхоо хувь заяаг даатгадаг. Ийнхүү өөр орчинд, өөр газарт тохиох адал явдал Нохой зээхийг улам бүр чангалж, илүү хүчирхэг болгодог.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/g7kdUy5_WlI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1430132" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1430132/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Wolverine (2013) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 126, 13, 'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation, Marvel Entertainment, Donners'' Company', '