(245, 'series', 'action;adventure;fantasy', 'Pirates of the Caribbean  Dead Man''s Chest', 'Карибын Тэнгисийн Дээрэмчид: Үхсэн Хүний Авдарт', 'pirates-of-the-caribbean-dead-man-s-chest-2006', '201411', 'd0489602f202835ad0313e8c52b14f9588e8848c.jpg', 2006, 0000, 'Jack Sparrow races to recover the heart of Davy Jones to avoid enslaving his soul to Jones'' service, as other friends and foes seek the heart for their own agenda as well.', 'Once again we''re plunged into the world of sword fights and "savvy" pirates. Captain Jack Sparrow is reminded he owes a debt to Davy Jones, who captains the flying Dutchman, a ghostly ship, with a crew from hell. Facing the "locker" Jack must find the heart of Davy Jones but to save himself he must get the help of quick-witted Will Turner and Elizabeth Swan. If that''s not complicated enough, Will and Elizabeth are sentenced to hang, unless will can get Lord Cutler Beckett Jack''s compass, Will is forced to join another crazy adventure with Jack.', 'Жэк Спароу өөрийн сүнсийг аврахын тулд Дэви Жөүнсийн зүрхийг эмчлэх аялалд гарна. Найзууд нь бас тус тусын шалтгаантайгаар түүний аялалд нэгддэг.', 'Жэк Спароу сүнслэг хөлгийн ахмад Дэви Жөүнсэд том өртэй. Энэ өрөө эс төлөвөөс өөрийн сүнсийг алдах аюултай тул тэр хуучны анд Вилл Тюрнерийн хамт дахин нэг аялалд гарна.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/ozk0-RHXtFw" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0383574" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0383574/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man''s Chest (2006) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/r