(246, 'series', 'fantasy', 'Pirates of the Caribbean  At World''s End', 'Карибын Тэнгисийн Дээрэмчид: Дэлхийн Төгсгөл Дээр', 'pirates-of-the-caribbean-at-world-s-end-2007', '201411', '1b473fcaf5437da2ac75b8a644797a283472fc2b.jpg', 2007, 0000, 'Captain Barbossa, Will Turner and Elizabeth Swann must sail off the edge of the map, navigate treachery and betrayal, and make their final alliances for one last decisive battle.', 'After Elizabeth, Will, and Captain Barbossa rescue Captain Jack Sparrow from the the land of the dead, they must face their foes, Davy Jones and Lord Cutler Beckett. Beckett, now with control of Jones'' heart, forms a dark alliance with him in order to rule the seas and wipe out the last of the Pirates. Now, Jack, Barbossa, Will, Elizabeth, Tia Dalma, and crew must call the Pirate Lords from the four corners of the globe, including the infamous Sao Feng, to gathering. The Pirate Lords want to release the goddess Calypso, Davy Jones''s damned lover, from the trap they sent her to out of fear, in which the Pirate Lords must combine the 9 pieces that bound her by ritual to undo it and release her in hopes that she will help them fight. With this, all pirates will stand together and will make their final stand for freedom against Beckett, Jones, Norrington, the Flying Dutchman, and the entire East India Trading Company', 'Ахмад Барбосса, Вилл Тюрнер, Элизабет Свон нар газрын зургийн төгсгөл хүртэл аялаж, урван тэрслэлтийг даван гарч, эцсийн тулаанд бэлтгэнэ.', 'Элизабет, Вилл, Ахмад Барбосса нар Жэк Спароуг үхэгсдийн арлаас аварч, мөнхийн дайсан Дэви Жөүнс, Катлер Бэккэт нартай эцсийн тулаанаа хийхээр зорино. Түүнийг ялахын тулд далайн дээрэмчдийн холбоо Дэви Жөүнсийн хайртай бүсгүйг зан үйлийн тусламжтайгаар эргэн сэргээж, эрх чөлөөгөө солилцохоор төлөвлөнө.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/PetrAmq9fcw" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0449088" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0449088/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Pirates of the Caribbean: At World''s End (2007) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 169, 13, 'Walt Disney Pictures, Jerry Bruckheimer Films, Second Mate Productions', 'Gore Verbinski', 'Ted Elliott, Terry Rossio,', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Pirates-of-the-caribbean-At-Worlds-End/218084918235683', 'http://pirates.disney.com/', '2007-05-25', 'Johnny Depp, Orlando Bloom, Keira Knightley', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-08 04:01:12', '2014-12-12 12:38:44'),
(247, 'series', 'action;adventure;fantasy', 'Pirates of the Caribbean  On Stranger Tides', 'Карибын Тэнгисийн Дээрэмчид: Давалгаан дээрх Үл Таних Хүн', 'pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-2011', '201411', '2d410786329ff3ca221aa2f1d32aec9feda9d435.jpg', 2011, 0000, 'Jack Sparrow and Barbossa embark on a quest to find the elusive fountain of youth, only to discover that Blackbeard and his daughter are after it too.', 'Captain Jack Sparrow (Depp) crosses paths with a woman from his past (Cruz), and he''s not sure if it''s love -- or if she''s a ruthless con artist who''s using him to find the fabled Fountain of Youth. When she forces him aboard the Queen Anne''s Revenge, the ship of the formidable pirate Blackbeard (McShane), Jack finds himself on an unexpected adventure in which he doesn''t know who to fear more: Blackbeard or the woman from his past', 'Жэк Спароу, Барбосса нар Мөнхийн Залуу Насны Ундаргыг хайж аялана. Гэтэл Блэкбөрд, Блэкбөрдийн охин хоёр бас адилхан зүйлийг хайж байгааг олж мэддэг.', 'Ахмад Жэк Спароу хуучин дурлалт бүсгүйтэйгээ эргэн учирна. Гэвч бүсгүй үнэхээр түүнд хайртай юу, эсвэл зүгээр л Мөнхийн Залуу Насны Ундаргыг олохдоо өөрийг нь ашиглаж байна уу гэдгийг үл мэднэ. Анне Хатны Хонзонт хөлгийн ахмад Блэкбөрдтэй тулах үедээ Жэк бүсгүй, ахмад хоёрын хэн нь илүү аюултай болохыг ойлгохыг хичээнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/KR_9A-cUEJc" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1298650" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1298650/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides (2011) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/imag