(251, 'movie', 'adventure', 'Troy', 'Трой', 'troy-2004', '201411', '1eed6a942004b640b6a1a41c98d21698f9adc935.jpg', 2004, 0000, 'An adaptation of Homer''s great epic, the film follows the assault on Troy by the united Greek forces and chronicles the fates of the men involved.', 'It is the year 1250 B.C. during the late Bronze age. Two emerging nations begin to clash after Paris, the Trojan prince, convinces Helen, Queen of Sparta, to leave her husband, Menelaus, and sail with him back to Troy. After Menelaus finds out that his wife was taken by the Trojans, he asks his brother Agamemnon to help him get her back. Agamemnon sees this as an opportunity for power. So they set off with 1,000 ships holding 50,000 Greeks to Troy. With the help of Achilles, the Greeks are able to fight the never before defeated Trojans. But they come to a stop by Hector, Prince of Troy. The whole movie shows their battle struggles and the foreshadowing of fate in this remake by Wolfgang Petersen of Homer''s "The Iliad.', 'Гомерийн агуу туульсаас сэдэвлэсэн энэ кинонд Трой хотыг Грекчүүд дайрсан түүх болоод тухайн үеийн баатруудын түүхийг өгүүлнэ.', 'Хүрэл зэвсгийн төгсгөл, МЭӨ 1250 он. Хүчирхэгжин тэлж буй хоёр үндэстний нүүр тулах цаг ирнэ. Трой хотын ханхуу Парис Менелаусын эхнэр, Спартагийн хатан Хеленийг нөхрөө хаяхыг ятгаж чадна. Эхнэрээ гутамшигтайгаар алдсан Менелаус дүү Агаменоны тусламжтайгаар Трой хотын зүг 1000 хөлөг онгоц, 50000 Грекийн дайчдыг аван хөдөлнө. Ахиллесийг армидаа нэгтгэсэн Грекчүүд Тройчуудтай эрэлхэгээр тулалдан, хэзээ ч ялж байгаагүй дайснаа буулгахад ойрхон ирлээ. Гэтэл тэднийг замд Тройгийн ханхүү Хектор саад болно. Гомерийн Илиадын түүхээс сэдэвлэсэн үйл явдал цаашид өрнөнө.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/znTLzRJimeY" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0332452" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0332452/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Troy (2004) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 163, 16, 'Warner Bros, Helena Productions, Latina Pictures', 'Wolfgang Petersen', 'Homer, David Benioff', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/Troy.Film', 'http://www.movie-locations.com/movies/t/Troy.html', '2004-05-14', 'Brad Pitt, Eric Bana, Orlando Bloom', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-08 04:31:47', '2014-12-10 08:33:59'),
(252, 'soap', 'action;adventure;drama;war', 'The Pacific', 'Номхон Далайд тулалдсан нь', 'the-pacific-2010', '201411', '9f72f7dbf2b8dc18d02aec8240c155a2fe31b268.jpg', 2010, 0000, 'The intertwined stories of three Marines during America''s battle with the Japanese in the Pacific during World War II.', 'The Pacific follows the lives of a U.S Marine Corps squad during the campaign within the Pacific against the Japanese Empire during WW2. Made by the creators of Band of Brothers, it follows a similar line of thought to outline the hardships of the common man during war. the Pacific is in parts a fast paced war series that can be enjoyed by action lovers whilst containing a more sensitive side when projecting the relationships (brotherhood) of Marines on the battlefield. where the Pacific takes a new direction from its "older brother" is in its depiction of the lives of soldiers who were picked to return home to increase the sales of war bonds, in doing this it also depicts the life cycle of returned soldiers from initial joy to the eventual feeling of regret and to a certain extent shame felt by soldiers wanting to return to the war in service of either their comrades or nation.', 'Дэлхийн 2-р дайны үед Америк-Японы дайнд оролцсон далайн цэргийн ангиудын түүхээс сэдэвлэн бүтээсэн олон ангит кино.', 'Ахан дүүс киног үргэлжлүүлэн бүтээсэн энэ олон ангит кинонд дайны цагийн хүнд хэцүүг харуулдаг. Номхон далайд байлдаж явсан энэ баатарлаг залуус ахан дүүсийн холбоо үүсгэж, хэдий дайнд эрэлхэгээр тулалдах ч гэртээ эргэн харих хүслээ бие биедээ дэлгэж, дайны дараа ч нөхөрлөлөө хадгалан үлдэж буй тухай өгүүлдэг.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e99B80crU3E', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0416449" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0416449/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="300 (2006) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(func