(256, 'series', 'action;fantasy;scifi', 'Underworld  Evolution', 'Доод Ертөнц: Хувьсал', 'underworld-evolution-2006', '201412', '9853a84f37ab4a9f6698dc57ad4d04975259aa34.jpg', 2006, 0000, 'Picking up directly from the previous film, vampire warrior Selene and the half werewolf Michael hunt for clues to reveal the history of their races and the war between them.', 'Underworld: Evolution continues the saga of war between the vampires and the Lycans. The film goes back to the beginnings of the ancient feud between the two tribes as Selene, the beautiful vampire heroine, and Michael, the lycan hybrid, try to unlock the secrets of their bloodlines. This will be a modern tale of action, intrigue and forbidden love, which takes them into the battle to end all wars as the immortals must finally face their retribution.', 'Цус сорогч, дайчин бүсгүй Селена, хүн чонын эрлийз Майкл нар өөрсдийн уг гарал, дайн дэгдсэн шалтгааныг олж мэдэх зорилготой аялалд гарна.', 'Цус сорогчид, хүн чоносын дайн үргэлжилсээр. Энэ дайны үүсэл зуу зуун жилийн өмнө амьдарч байсан ноёлогчдын зөрчилдөөнөөс үүссэн байлаа. Ийнхүү дурлалт хосууд хайр дурлалаа өс хонзонт хоёр овог аймгийн дайны золиос болгохгүйн тулд дайныг зогсоохоор тэмцэнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/mQ8c4bGFmQc" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0401855" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0401855/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Underworld: Evolution (2006) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 106, 16, 'Screen Gems, Lakeshore Entertainment', 'Len Wiseman', 'Danny McBride (screenplay), Len Wiseman', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/underworldevolution', 'http://www.lakeshore-records.com/underworld_evolution/index.html', '2006-01-20', 'Kate Beckinsale, Scott Speedman, Bill Nighy', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-08 07:06:20', '2014-12-12 12:37:16');
