(257, 'series', 'action;adventure;fantasy', 'Underworld  Rise of the Lycans', 'Доод Ертөнц: Хүн Чоносын Бослого', 'underworld-rise-of-the-lycans-2009', '201412', 'd9c75eda7f306294a70317a33bce42e03df9a88e.jpg', 2009, 0000, 'An origins story centered on the centuries-old feud between the race of aristocratic vampires and their onetime slaves, the Lycans.', 'The prequel story traces the origins of the centuries-old blood feud between the aristocratic vampires and their onetime slaves, the Lycans. In the Dark Ages, a young Lycan named Lucian emerges as a powerful leader who rallies the werewolves to rise up against Viktor, the cruel vampire king who has enslaved them. Lucian is joined by his secret lover, Sonja, in his battle against the Vampire army and his struggle for Lycan freedom.', 'Хүн чонос үүрд мөнхийн боолчлолоос гарахын тулд цус сорогчдын эсрэг дайн эхлүүлнэ. Эрх чөлөөнийхөө төлөө тэмцэгч хүн чоностой зарим цус сорогчид нэгдэнэ.', 'Зуу зуун жил үргэлжилсэн цуст дайны үүсэл нь цус сорогчид хүн чоносыг боолчилж байсан Харанхуй Цаг үед эхэлжээ. Лусиан нэрт хүчирхэг хүн чоно харгис хэрцгий цус сорогчдын хааны эсрэг бослого гаргахад Лусианы хайртай бүсгүй Сониа энэ дайнд Лусианы талд ордог.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/8pQeN9l5WWs" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0834001" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0834001/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Underworld: Rise of the Lycans (2009) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 92, 16, 'Sketch Films, Lakeshore Entertainment, Screen Gems', 'Patrick Tatopoulos', 'Danny McBride (screenplay), Dirk Blackman', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/EnterTheUnderworld', 'http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/underworldawakening/', '2009-01-23', 'Rhona Mitra, Michael Sheen, Bill Nighy', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-08 07:10:49', '2014-12-12 12:37:06'),
(258, 'series', 'action;fantasy;horror', 'Underworld  Awakening', 'Доод Ертөнц: Сэргэлт', 'underworld-awakening-2012', '201412', '0b9e670652b655bb87604bdecac5af5a98aec395.jpg', 2012, 0000, 'When human forces discover the existence of the Vampire and Lycan clans, a war to eradicate both species commences. The vampire warrior Selene leads the battle against humankind.', 'Mankind discover the existence of the Vampire and Lycan species and they begin a war to annihilate the races. When Selene meets with Michael in the harbor, they are hit by a grenade and Selene passes out. Twelve years later, Selene awakes from a cryogenic sleep in the Antigen laboratory and meets the Vampire David. She learns that she had been the subject of the scientist Dr. Jacob Lane and the Vampire and Lycan species have been practically eradicated from Earth. But Selene is still connected to Michael and has visions that she believes that belongs to Michael''s sight. However she has a surprise and finds that she has a powerful daughter named Eve that has been raised in the laboratory. Now Selene and David have to protect Eve against the Lycans that intend to use her to inoculate their species against silver', 'Хүн төрөлхтөн цус сорогч, хүн чоносын төрөлтөн амьд мэнд байгааг мэдээд тэднийг устгаж үгүй хийх дайн эхлүүлнэ. Цус сорогч дайчин бүсгүй Селена тэдний эсрэг дайныг удирдана.', 'Хүн төрөлхтний эсрэг дайнд нэгдсэн Селена бүсгүй бөмбөгөнд өртөж, ухаан алдана. 12 жилийн дараа тэрээр судалгааны лабораторид сэрдэг. Цус сорогчид болон хүн чонос дайнд ялагдаж, устаж үгүй болж буй бөгөөд Селенаг доктор Жэкоб Жэйн судалгааны зорилгоор авч үлдсэн болохыг мэднэ. Гэвч Селена Майклтай холбоотой хэвээрээ л байдаг. Удалгүй Селенад Ева нэртэй охиныг нь авчирч өгөхөд учир битүүлэг зүүднийхээ утгыг ойлгодог. Гэтэл хүн чоносууд Еваг ашиглаж, овог удмаа сэргээхээр төлөвлөнө. Одоо Селена тэднээс охиноо хамгаалах ёстой.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/tUcrbUCWKQc" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1496025" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1496025/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Underworld: Awakening (2012) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 88, 16, 'Screen Gems, Lakeshore Entertainment, Saturn Films', 'Mans Marlind, Bjorn Stein', 'Len Wiseman, John Hlavin', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/Underworld', 'http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/underworldawakening/', '2012-01-20', 'Kate Beckinsale, Michael Ealy, India Eisley', '', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-08 07:24:41', '2014-12-12 12:37:00'),
(259, 'movie', 'crime;drama', 'Green Street Hooligans', 'Ногоон гудамжны хулигаанууд', 'green-street-hooligans-2005', '201412', 'fc84e13be99830176c21b7936299477bba18d90c.jpg', 2005, 0000, 'A wrongfully expelled Harvard undergrad moves to London, where he is introduced to the violent underworld of football hooliganism.', 'Unjustly expelled from Harvard when a stash of cocaine is found in his possession, Matt moves to London to live with his sister and her husband Steve. He is quickly introduced to Steve''s chirpy, cock-sure younger brother Pete. Initially, Pete is reluctant to get acquainted with Matt and allow him to tread around the capital city with him because he may be seen by others as an ''outsider'', but after a heavy drinking session with him and his mates he quickly changes his opinion of him. On the way back from a football match, Matt is viciously accosted by a gang of Birmingham City thugs, until Pete and his friends step in and save him. It is from here that Matt learns the truth about Pete and his friends- they are football hooligans, operating the GSE (Green Street Elite) ''firm.'' Initially afraid of the violence, Matt soon ends up becoming as desensitized to it as his new found friends - but as events roll on, suspicion, shocking revelations and unsettled scores combine to a devastating', 'Харвардын сургуулиас хилсээр хөөгдсөн оюутан Лондон хотод очиж, хөлбөмбөгийн хулигаануудтай танилцана.', 'Санаандгүй байдлаар хар тамхины хэрэгт хилсээр холбогдсон Мэт Харвардын сургуулиас хөөгдөж, Лондонд амьдардаг эгчийнхээ гэр бүл дээр очно. Удалгүй тэрээр эгчийнх нь нөхөр Стивийн дүү Пететэй танилцаж, нөхөрлөдөг. Гэтэл Пете Ногоон Гудамжны Хулигаанууд нэртэй хөлбөмбөгийн багийн дэмжигчид болохыг олж мэддэг.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/EAe-1Lv1KYU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0385002" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0385002/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Green Street Hooligans (2005) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 109, 16, 'Baker Street, OddLot Entertainment, Yank Film Finane,Universal pictures', 'Lexi Alexander', 'Lexi Alexander, Dougie Brimson', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Green-Street-Hooligans/9369849261', 'http://www.warnervideo.com/greenstreethooligans/', '2005-09-09', 'Elijah Wood, Charlie Hunnam, Claire Forlani', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-08 07:41:35', '2014-12-12 06:55:20'),
(260, 'movie', 'action;comedy;scifi', 'R.I.P.D', 'Үл үхэгсдийн цагдаагийн газар', 'r-i-p-d-2013', '201412', '478c57b3c7c640396d066ce7fd128a8f990cb819.jpg', 2013, 0000, 'A recently slain cop joins a team of undead police officers working for the Rest in Peace Department and tries to find the man who murdered him', 'After Nick is murdered by his own partner, he joins the Rest in Peace Department to protect the world from the undeads. While working with his new partner, many undeads are seen gathering in Boston. Soon he realizes that someone close to him is behind all a plot to bring on the apocalypse.', 'Өөд болоод удаагүй нэгэн цагдаа үл үхэгсдийн цагдаагийн газарт ажилд орж, өөрийг нь хороосон гэмт хэрэгтний араас явна.', 'Никийг өөрийнх нь хамтрагч буудан хороодог. Ийнхүү тэр үл үхэгсдийн цагдаагийн газарт ажилд орж, дэлхий ертөнцийг үл үхэгсдээс хамгаалах үүрэг хүлээнэ. Учир нь үл үхэгсэд Бостон хотод цугларч, том ажиллагаа зохион байгуулахаар бэлтгэж байдаг. Гэтэл энэ бүхний ард түүний дотны хүн байх нь тэр.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/X07xNrVd7DU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0790736" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0790736/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="R.I.P.D. (2013) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 96, 13, 'Universal Pictures, Original Film, Dark Horse Entertainment', 'Robert Schwentke', 'Phil Hay, Matt Manfredi', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/RIPD?_fb_noscript=1', 'http://www.universalstudiosentertainment.com/ripd/', '2013-07-19', 'Ryan Reynolds, Jeff Bridges, Mary-Louise Parker', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-08 09:02:12', '2014-12-12 06:51:57'),
(261, 'series', 'action;comedy;crime', 'RED 2', 'ТГАЭ - Тэтгэвэрт гарсан аюултай этгээдүүд 2', 'red-2-2013', '201412', '8dca17fb2e14c41303f2f4214bbea9680056e3b1.jpg', 2013, 0000, 'Retired C.I.A. agent Frank Moses reunites his unlikely team of elite operatives for a global quest to track down a missing portable nuclear device.', 'Retired CIA agent Frank Moses is in love with Sarah Ross and enjoying their normal life. Out of the blue, Marvin Boggs meets Frank in the supermarket and tells that Wikileaks has released the information that they had participated and know the whereabouts of the Nightshade, a portable nuclear weapon that was smuggled in pieces and hidden in Russia. Now the top agents in the world are under contract to seek them out to discover where Nightshade is. The trio travels to Paris and teams-up with the Russian Katja to track down the former Russian Agent ''The Frog'' to get more information about the operation. They learn that the brilliant inventor Dr. Edward Bailey might know where the weapon is. They discover that Bailey has been interned in an asylum in London by the MI-16 for thirty-two years and the British Victoria joins the team. They rescue Bailey and find that the nuclear device is hidden in the Kremlin. Soon the dangerous South Korean Han joins the group expecting to retrieve the', 'Тэтгэвэртээ гарсан тагнуулч Фрэнк Мозес алдагдсан цөмийн бөмбөгийг хайж, дэлхий тойрох аялалдаа хуучин андуудыгаа нэгтгэдэг.', 'Тагнуулын төв газрын хуучин тагнуул Фрэнк Мозес, Сара Росс нар амар тайван амьдралдаа эргэн оржээ. Гэтэл дэлгүүрт санаандгүй таарсан Марвин Богс түүнд алдагдсан цөмийн зэвсгийн талаар хэлдэг. Ингээд хуучны андууд Орост байгаа цөмийн зэвсгийг олохоор гэрээ байгуулна. Эхлээд тэд Парист очиж, Оросын Катятай уулзах бөгөөд Оросын "Мэлхий" нэрт тагнуулын талаар илүү мэдээлэл олж авдаг. Эцэст нь тэд аюулт зэвсгийг Кремлийн ордонд нуусан гэдгийг илрүүлнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/sCM3HhGUJsM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1821694" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1821694/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="RED 2 (2013) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 116, 13, 'Summit Entertainment, Di Bonaventura Pictures, DC Entertainment', 'Dean Parisot', 'Jon Hoeber, Erich Hoeber', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/RED', 'http://www.red-themovie.com/', '2013-07-19', 'Bruce Willis, Helen Mirren, John Malkovich', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-08 09:08:02', '2014-12-12 12:36:53'),
(262, 'series', 'action;comedy;crime', 'RED', 'ТГАЭ - Тэтгэвэрт гарсан аюултай этгээдүүд', 'red-2010', '201412', '7f8c476c92526bd15548a039b7ad629fdab54dae.jpg', 2010, 0000, 'When his peaceful life is threatened by a high-tech assassin, former black-ops agent Frank Moses reassembles his old team in a last ditch effort to survive and uncover his assailants.', 'Frank (Bruce Willis) is retired, bored and lonely living off his government pension in a nondescript suburb in an equally nondescript house. The only joy in Frank''s life are his calls to the government pension processing center when he gets to talk to his case worker Sarah (Mary-Louis Parker). Sarah is as bored and lonely as Frank and marks her conversations with the unknown Frank and her spy novels as the only things fun in her life. When something in Frank''s past forces Frank back into his old line of work and puts an unwitting Sarah in the middle of the intrigue, Frank and Sarah begin a journey into Frank''s past and the people he used to work with. Like Frank they are all RED ... Retired Extremely Dangerous.', 'Амар тайван амьдралыг нь үгүй хийсэн мэргэжлийн алуурчнаас амиа аврахын тулд Фрэнк Мозес хуучны андуутайгаа холбоо барина.', 'Тусгай албанаас тэтгэвэртээ гарсан Фрэнкийн амьдрал ерөнхийдөө л нэгэн хэвийн, уйтгартай. Түүний цорын ганц сонирхдог зүйл нь нийгмийн даатгалын ажилтан Саратай ярилцах байдаг. Харин Сарагийн хувьд амьдрал бас л уйтгартай. Тиймээс тэр нууц тагнуулын тухай ном уншиж, тийм хүнтэй учрахыг сэмхэн мөрөөдөж явдаг. Гэтэл нэгэн өдөр Фрэнкийг хөнөөхөөр мэргэжлийн алуурчин ирсэн нь түүнийг хуучны андуудтайгаа холбоо барихад хүргэдэг. Гэтэл энэ хэрэгт Сара өөрөө ч мэдэлгүй холбогдож орхино.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/rMCh4etBbkU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1245526" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1245526/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="RED (