(264, 'series', 'action;adventure;thriller', 'Live Free or Die Hard', 'Хатуу самар: Эрх чөлөөт амьдрал', 'live-free-or-die-hard-2007', '201412', '8bcecbeb1dcc9e6d265a8312b356c5c3763a1c0b.jpg', 2007, 0000, 'John McClane and a young hacker join forces to take down master cyber-terrorist Thomas Gabriel in Washington D.C.', 'When someone hacks into the computers at the FBI''s Cyber Crime Division; the Director decides to round up all the hackers who could have done this. When he''s told that because it''s the 4th of July most of their agents are not around so they might have trouble getting people to get the hackers. So he instructs them to get local PD''S to take care of it. And one of the cops they ask is John McClane who is tasked with bringing a hacker named Farrell to the FBI. But as soon as he gets there someone starts shooting at them. McClane manages to get them out but they''re still being pursued. And it''s just when McClane arrives in Washington that the whole system breaks down and chaos ensues.', 'Жон МкКлэйн, хакер залуутай хамтран Томас Габриель гэх кибер гэмт хэрэгтнийг илрүүлнэ.', 'Холбооны мөрдөх товчооны Кибер гэмт хэрэгтэй тэмцэх хэлтсийн компьютерт нэгэн хакер нэвтэрдэг. Үүнийг мэдсэн товчооны захирал бүх хакеруудыг шалгахаар шийднэ. Гэвч 7 сарын 4-ны өдөр мөрдөгчид амралтаа авсан байх тул цагдаагийн газартай хамтрахаар болдог. Цагдаагийн газарт МкКлэйнд Фарель нэртэй хакерыг баривчилж ирэх тушаал өгнө. Хаягын дагуу очтол шууд өөдөөс нь галлана.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/8Jz-8UcCiws" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0337978" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0337978/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Live Free or Die Hard (2007) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[