(266, 'movie', 'action;adventure;comedy', 'Zathura: A Space Adventure', 'Затура: Сансрын адал явдал', 'zathura-a-space-adventure-2005', '201412', '5db4d360cc569d4a70c4b59bf044a252a0b722f5.jpg', 2005, 0000, 'Two young brothers are drawn into an intergalactic adventure when their house is hurled through the dephs of space by the magical board game they are playing.', 'Danny and Walter are two brothers who barely get along even while driving their parents to distraction as their older sister tries to ignore them. Despite their squabbling, the brothers manage cooperate enough to play an old mechanical board game named Zathura. However, after their first move, they find that the game has apparently flung them, their sister and their entire house into outer space. Furthermore, the brothers surmise the only way to return home is to finish the game. However with almost every move, new dangers arise as the siblings find themselves learning to cooperate in ways they never expected as they realize what they mean to each other.', 'Ах дүү хоёр ид шидийн хөлөгт тоглоом тоглож эхэлтэл гэр нь сансрын уудамд татагдан ордог.', 'Дэнни, Волтер хоёр ах дүү мөртлөө огт таарахгүй. Байнга л маргалдаж байдаг. Тэд нэгэн өдөр Затура нэртэй хөлөгт тоглоом тоглоно. Гэтэл тоглоом эхэлмэгц л тэдний байшин сансрын уудамд татагдан ордог. Гэртээ харих цор ганц арга нь тоглоомыг дуустал нь тоглох учраас тэд зориглон дараагийн нүүдлийг хийнэ. Гэвч нүүдэл бүр хоёр хүүд болон эгчид нь аюул дагуулна. Энэ аймшигт адал явдал ах дүү хоёрыг, эгчийг нь бие биедээ сайн хандаж, хоорондоо таарамжтай байхад сургадаг.', '<iframe width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/c_pI6s8W7P0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0406375" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0406375/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Zathura: A Space Adventure (2005) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 101, 6, 'Columbia Pictures Corporation, Radar Pictures, Teitler Film', 'Jon Favreau', 'Chris Van Allsburg, David Koepp', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/Zathura', 'https://www.facebook.com/Zathura', '2005-11-11', 'Josh Hutcherson, Jonah Bobo, Dax Shepard', 'http://kickass.so/zathura-a-space-adventure-2005-1080p-brrip-x264-yify-t7223892.html', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/Zathura', 2, 2, '2014-12-09 06:22:44', '2014-12-12 05:59:09'),
(267, 'movie', 'adventure;family;fantasy', 'The Spiderwick Chronicles', 'Спайдервикийн Түүх', 'the-spiderwick-chronicles-2008', '201412', '321033763de766e506bc2c6d309d46351aa0810f.jpg', 2008, 0000, 'Upon moving into the run-down Spiderwick Estate with their mother, twin brothers Jared and Simon Grace, along with their sister Mallory, find themselves pulled into an alternate world full of faeries and other creatures.', 'Once upon a time, upon moving into the run-down Spiderwick Estate with their mother, twin brothers Jared and Simon Grace, along with their sister Mallory, find themselves pulled into an alternate world full of faeries and other creatures. Unable to explain the strange disappearances and accidents that seem to be happening on a daily basis, the family blames it all on Jared. When he, Simon and Mallory investigate what''s really going on, they uncover the fantastic truth of the Spiderwick estate and of the creatures that inhabit it.', 'Спайдервикийн эдлэнд нүүж ирсэн ихэр ах дүү Жэрид, Симон, Мэллори нар ид шидийн амьтад, өөр бусад аймшигт биетүүдээр дүүрэн өөр нэг ертөнц байдгыг олж мэднэ.', 'Гэрт нь тохиолдсон бүх хачирхалтай явдалд Жэридийг буруутгана. Гэвч эцэст нь тэд Спайдервикийн эдлэнгийн нууцыг дэлгэж, шидэт номыг аврах аялалд гардаг.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/EAZhi4LlDAw" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0416236" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0416236/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Spiderwick Chronicles (2008) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 96, 9, 'Paramount Pictures, Nickelodeon Movies, Kennedy/Marshall Company', 'Mark Waters', 'Karey Kirkpatrick (screenplay), David Berenbaum (screenplay)', 0, 0, '', 'http://www.ascronicasdespiderwick.com.br', '2008-02-14', 'Freddie Highmore, Sarah Bolger, David Strathairn', 'http://kickass.so/the-spiderwick-chronicles-2008-dvdrip-axxo-t207215.html', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.ascronicasdespiderwick.com.br', 2, 2, '2014-12-09 06:25:54', '2014-12-12 05:55:40'),
(268, 'movie', 'adventure;family;fantasy', 'The Golden Compass', 'Алтан Луужин', 'the-golden-compass-2007', '201412', '596bedfbfd847e3be7d6dc171a3df53ccd8a677d.jpg', 2007, 0000, 'In a parallel universe, young Lyra Belacqua journeys to the far North to save her best friend and other kidnapped children from terrible experiments by a mysterious organization.', 'In a parallel world ruled by The Magisterium where people''s souls have animal shapes, the orphan Lyra Belaqua is educated in the Jordan College, and her uncle and Professor Lord Asriel is her tutor. Lyra accidentally overhears a conversation about a research of Lord Asriel in the North Artic and the existence of a powerful Dust that unites different worlds. When her best friend Roger is kidnapped by the evil Gobblers, Lyra promises to rescue him. She is invited to go to the North with the influent Mrs. Coulter and the Jordan''s Vice-Chancellor secretly gives her a magic golden compass capable of revealing the truth. When Lyra finds that Mrs. Coulter is the leader of the Gobblers, she escapes from her house and the runaway girl begins an amazing adventure in a war to save her friend and other missing children with her allied Gyptians, Witches and the strong Armored Bear Iorek Byrnison.', 'Манай дэлхийн паралель ертөнцөд Лира Бэликуа нэрт бяцхан охин алс умардын нутагт аялаж, хамгийн сайн найзыгаа бусад хулгайлагдсан хүүхдүүдийн хамт аварна.', 'Лира Бэлакуа нэрт бяцхан охин хойд мөсөн далайд байдаг шидэт тоосонцор бүх дэлхийг нэгтгэх хүчтэй тухай сэм сонсоно. Гэтэл удалгүй түүний доны найз Рожерийг Гоблерууд хулгайлдаг. Найзыгаа аврахаар умардыг зорих Лирад Хадагтай Колтер алтан луужин өгч, зөв зам олоход нь тусална хэмээн амална. Яг үнэндээ Хадагтай Колтер Гоблеруудын удирдагч байдаг. Тиймээс Лира Колтерийн шилтгээнээс зугтаж, шидтэнүүд, хуягт баавгай нартай хамтран адал явдлаар дүүрэн аялалдаа гардаг.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/3KUscLoqqAY" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0385752" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0385752/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Golden Compass (2007) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 113, 6, 'New Line Cinema, Ingenious Film Partners, Scholastic Productions', 'Chris Weitz', 'Chris Weitz (screenplay), Philip Pullman (novel)', 0, 0, '', 'http://www.warnerbros.com/', '2007-12-07', 'Nicole Kidman, Daniel Craig, Dakota Blue Richards', 'http://kickass.so/the-golden-compass-2007-dvdrip-xvid-btsfilms-t1157921.html', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.warnerbros.com/', 2, 2, '2014-12-09 06:34:26', '2014-12-11 12:11:13'),
(269, 'series', 'adventure;family;fantasy', 'The Chronicles of Narnia: The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe', 'Нарниагийн Домог: Арслан, Шидтэн ба Шидэт Шүүгээ', 'the-chronicles-of-narnia-the-lion-the-witch-and-the-wardrobe-2005', '201412', 'd5f3d55ec09153892f6014f9eda22a22a3efb169.jpg', 2005, 0000, 'Four kids travel through a wardrobe to the land of Narnia and learn of their destiny to free it with the guidance of a mystical lion.', 'When the Pevensie family are evacuated out to the country, they are unaware of the adventure they will encounter. During a game of hide and seek, the youngest daughter, Lucy (Henley) discovers a wardrobe which transports her to the land of Narnia. Covered in snow, Narnia is full of weird and wonderful creatures, but is watched over by the evil White Witch, Jadis (Swinton). When all four Pevensie children end up through the wardrobe, they discover that it was meant to be, as two daughters of Eve and two sons of Adam must join with the mighty lion, Aslan (Neeson) to defeat the evil White Witch.', 'Певенсие гэр бүлийн дөрвөн хүүхэд нуугдаж тоглож байгаад үлгэрийн хаант улс Нарниа руу нэвтрэх хаалгыг олдог. Тэнд хүүхдүүд арслангаар газарчлуулан, өөрсдийн хувь төөрөгөө олно.', 'Цасанд хучигдсан Нарниагийн хаант улсад хачин жигтэй, гайхамшигтай амьтад олон бий. Гэвч тэд бүгд хорон санаат Цагаан Шидтэний хараанд амьдардаг. Санаандгүй Нарниад ирсэн дөрвөн хүүхэд анхнаасаа л Цагаан Шидтэнийг ялж, Нарниагийн улсад сайн цагийг авчрах тавилантай байжээ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/LshOd31d-yE" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0363771" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0363771/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Chronicles of Narnia: The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe (2005) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 143, 6, 'Walt Disney Pictures, Walden Media', 'Andrew Adamson', 'Ann Peacock (screenplay), Andrew Adamson (screenplay)', 0, 0, '', 'http://movies.disney.com/the-chronicles-of-narnia-the-lion-the-witch-and-the-wardrobe', '2005-12-09', 'Tilda Swinton, Georgie Henley, William Moseley', 'http://kickass.so/the-chronicles-of-narnia-the-lion-the-witch-and-the-wardrobe-2005-1080p-brrip-x264-yify-t7243275.html', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'http://movies.disney.com/the-chronicles-of-narnia-the-lion-the-witch-and-the-wardrobe', 2, 2, '2014-12-09 06:37:18', '2014-12-11 11:33:59'),
(270, 'series', 'action;adventure;family', 'The Chronicles of Narnia: Prince Caspian', 'Нарниагийн Домог: Каспийн Ханхүү', 'the-chronicles-of-narnia-prince-caspian-2008', '201412', 'b762d11ab9885a236885a1f2ec87011fdfcba574.jpg', 2008, 0000, 'The Pevensie siblings return to Narnia, where they are enlisted to once again help ward off an evil king and restore the rightful heir to the land''s throne, Prince Caspian.', 'The four Pevensie children return to Narnia, only to discover that hundreds of years have passed since they ruled there, and the evil King Miraz has taken charge. With the help of a heroic mouse called Reepicheep, and the exiled heir to the throne, Prince Caspian, they set out to overthrow the King, once again with Aslan''s help.', 'Певенсиегийн гэр бүл Нарниад эргэн ирж, хорон санаат хааныг засаглалаас түлхэн унагаж, зүй ёсны өв залгамжлагч Каспиан Ханхүүг Нарниагийн эзэн хааны суудалд өргөмжлөнө.', 'Певенсиегийн хүүхдүүд Нарниад эргэн иртэл тэдний өмнө ирсэн үеэс хэдэн зуун жил өнгөрч, Мираз нэрт хорон санаат хаан төрийн эрхийг авсан байхтай таарна. Тэд Рипишип нэрт хулгана, арслангийн тусламжтай, зүй ёсны өв залгамжлагч ханхүү Каспианыг хаан ширээнд суулгана.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/9Q0Da4jlxBk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0499448" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0499448/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Chronicles of Narnia: Prince Caspian (2008) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 150, 6, 'Walt Disney Pictures, Walden Media, Ozumi Films', 'Andrew Adamson', 'ndrew Adamson (screenplay), Christopher Markus (screenplay)', 0, 0, '', 'https://www.narnia.com/us', '2008-05-16', 'Ben Barnes, Skandar Keynes, Georgie Henley', 'http://kickass.so/the-chronicles-of-narnia-prince-caspian-2008-1080p-brrip-x264-yify-t7243284.html', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'https://www.narnia.com/us', 2, 2, '2014-12-09 06:40:42', '2014-12-11 11:37:38'),
(271, 'series', 'adventure;family;fantasy', 'The Chronicles of Narnia: The Voyage of the Dawn Treader', 'Нарниагийн Домог: Үүрийн Гэгээ Хөлгөөр Аялсан нь', 'the-chronicles-of-narnia-the-voyage-of-the-dawn-treader-2010', '201412', '1933a04579642dc6bd191d7236aa15d2a39e19e1.jpg', 2010, 0000, 'Lucy and Edmund Pevensie return to Narnia with their cousin Eustace where they meet up with Prince Caspian for a trip across the sea aboard the royal ship The Dawn Treader. Along the way they encounter dragons, dwarves, merfolk, and a band of lost warriors before reaching the edge of the world.', 'Lucy and Edmund Pevensie are stranded in Cambridge, living in the house of their obnoxious cousin Eustace, while the grown-ups Susan and Peter are living in the USA with their parents. When a painting of a ship sailing on the sea of Narnia overflows water in their room, Lucy, Edmund and Eustace are transported to the ocean of Narnia and rescued by King Caspian and the crew of the ship The Dawn Treader. Caspian explains that Narnia has been in peace for three years but before he took his throne back, his uncle tried to kill the seven lords of Telmar, who were the closest and most loyal friends of his father. They fled to The Lone Island and no one has ever heard anything about them. Now Caspian is seeking out the lords of Telmar with his Captain Drinian, the talking mouse Reepicheep and his loyal men. Soon, they discover that an evil form of green mist is threatening Narnia and the siblings and their cousin join Caspian in a quest to retrieve the seven swords of the seven lords of ...', 'Люси, Эдмунд Певенсие хоёр үсэл Иустэйсийн хамт ханхүү Каспианы "Үүрийн Гэгээ" хөлгөөр их далайг туулах аялалд гарна. Тэдний аялал адал явдлаар дүүрэн байж, луу, одойчууд, лусын хүмүүс, ялагдсан дайчидтай тааралдаж, эцэст нь ертөнцийн хязгаарт хүрдэг.', 'Люси Нарниагийн далайн зургийг зурж байтал их ус гэнэт гарч ирж, тэд жинхэнэ Нарниад ирсэн байна. Тэднийг Каспиан ханхүү "Үүрийн Гэгээ" хөлөгтэйгээ ирж авардаг. Каспиан тэдэнд Нарниад тохиолдсон үйл явдлуудыг хүүрнэх зуур Тельмарын долоон түшмэдийг хайж, алсын аялалд гарах болсон тухайгаа хэлнэ. Певенсиегийн гэр бүл дахин нэг удаа Нарниагийн хаант улсыг аварна.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/2rC9Zxj0EJo" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt0980970" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0980970/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Chronicles of Narnia: The Voyage of the Dawn Treader (2010) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 113, 6, 'Fox 2000 Pictures, Walden Media, Dune Entertainment', 'Michael Apted', 'Christopher Markus, Stephen McFeely', 0, 0, '', 'https://www.narnia.com/us', '2010-12-10', 'Ben Barnes, Skandar Keynes, Georgie Henley', 'http://kickass.so/the-chronicles-of-narnia-the-voyage-of-the-dawn-treader-2010-1080p-brrip-x264-yify-t7243292.html', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'https://www.narnia.com/us', 2, 2, '2014-12-09 06:43:18', '2014-12-11 11:46:24');
