(287, 'series', 'horror', 'The Texas Chainsaw Massacre', 'Техасын хөрөөтэй алуурчин', 'the-texas-chainsaw-massacre-2003', '201412', 'fddbe99c469af2b65090f1bf940e51f7d9ad9588.jpg', 2003, 0000, 'After picking up a traumatized young hitchhiker, five friends find themselves stalked and hunted by a deformed chainsaw-wielding killer and his family of equally psychopathic killers.', 'Driving through the backwoods of Texas, five youths pick up a traumatized hitchhiker, who shoots herself in their van. Shaken by the suicide, the group seeks help from the locals, but their situation becomes even more surreal when they knock on the door of a remote homestead. It''s quickly apparent the residents are a family of inbred psychopaths, and the unlucky youths suddenly find themselves running for their lives. In hot pursuit is a disfigured, chainsaw-wielding cannibal known as Leatherface.', 'Замын хүнийг машиндаа суулгасан таван залуу удалгүй аймшигт цуврал алуурчны бай болдог.', 'Таван найз Техасын замд гар өргөсөн нэгэн хүнийг машиндаа суулгана. Гэтэл ухаан алдатлаа айсан хүн машин дотор амиа хорлодог. Айж сандарсан хүүхдүүд нэгэн айлын хаалгыг тогшиж, тусламж хүснэ. Гэтэл тэр нь хүний махаар хооллогч аймшигт цуврал алуурчдын байшин байдаг. Тэдний ахлагч нь Арьсанбагт алуурчин юм.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/dg3LWY70rvw" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0324216" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0324216/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Texas Chainsaw Massacre (2003) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 98, 18, 'New Line Cinema, Focus Features, Radar Pictures', 'Marcus Nispel', 'Kim Henkel, Tobe Hooper', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/leatherfacefamily', 'http://www.thetexaschainsawmassacre.net/', '2003-10-17', 'Jessica Biel, Jonathan Tucker, Andrew Bryniarski', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-10 03:03:20', '2014-12-12 09:36:46'),
(288, 'series', 'horror', 'The Texas Chainsaw Massacre  The Beginning', 'Техасын хөрөөтэй алуурчин: Эхлэл', 'the-texas-chainsaw-massacre-the-beginning-2006', '201412', '7cd2f165d49f8016e195e781d89088a25635f218.jpg', 2006, 0000, 'On one last road trip before they''re sent to serve in Vietnam, two brothers and their girlfriends get into an accident that calls their local sheriff to the scene. Thus begins a terrifying experience where the teens are taken to a secluded house of horrors, where a young, would-be killer is being nurtured.', 'In August, 1939, a worker goes into labor while working in a slaughterhouse and dies after a complicated labor, though the deformed child survives. The possibly orphaned baby is dumped in a garbage container and found by a beggar later, who brings him home. Along the years, the mentally retarded and disturbed boy called Thomas is raised by the Hewitt family in spite of having psychological problems as well as suffering from an unnamed skin disorder, later working in a meat packing plant. In July, 1969, when the facility is closed, the inhabitants move to other places, but the deformed, mentally childlike Thomas flies into a rage after being insulted and kills the foreman. His deranged brother (considered his uncle due to their age difference) executes the sheriff that is going to arrest Thomas, and assumes his identity, wearing his clothes,driving his car though the roads in Texas and entitling himself as Sheriff Hoyt. Meanwhile, the brothers Eric and Dean are traveling in a Jeep with', 'Вьетнамд алба хаахаар явахынхаа өмнө сүүлчийн аялалдаа гарсан ах дүү хоёр найз охиныгоо авч явдаг. Гэтэл замд осол гарч, орон нутгийн цагдааг дуудна. Харамсалтай нь цагдаагийн хувцас өмссөн хүн ирээдүйн цуврал алуурчин байлаа.', '1939 он. Яргачдын байшинд нэгэн бүсгүй төрж, төрсөн даруйдаа өөд болсон ч тахир дутуу хүүхэд нь амьд үлддэг. Гэвч амьд үлдсэн хүүхдийг хогийн саванд хаясныг нэгэн тэнүүлч хүн олж, гэртээ авчирдаг. Сэтгэцийн өвчтэй, нэр нь үл мэдэгдэх арьсны халдвар авсан Томас хүүг Хэвитийн гэр бүл том болтол нь өсгөж, эцэст нь мах бэлтгэх үйлдвэрт ажилд оруулдаг. 1969 оны 7-р сард мах бэлтгэлийн үйлдвэр хаагдахад ажилчид нь өөр газар руу нүүнэ. Харин өвчтэй, сэтгэцийн хувьд хүүхдээс ялгаагүй Томас доромжлуулж, эцэст нь өөрийг нь доромжилсон хүнийг хороодог. Тэгээд өөрийг нь баривчлахаар ирсэн цагдааг баривчилж, хувцсыг өмсөж, машиныг нь авч зугтаадаг.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/2OKXd2j6Fmo" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0420294" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0420294/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Texas Chainsaw Massacre: The Beginning (2006) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 146, 18, 'New Line Cinema, Platinum Dunes, Next Entertainment', 'Jonathan Liebesman', 'Sheldon Turner, Sheldon Turner', 0, 0, 'https://de-de.facebook.com/pages/The-Texas-Chainsaw-Massacre-The-Beginning/168598619555', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Texas_Chainsaw_Massacre:_The_Beginning', '2006-10-06', 'Jordana Brewster, Matt Bomer, Diora Baird', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 2, 2, '2014-12-10 03:10:56', '2014-12-12 10:21:20');
