(367, 'series', 'action;drama;history;war', 'Red Cliff II', 'Улаан эрэг 2', 'red-cliff-ii-2009', '201412', '9d337b04414fb7ebed94cf23d9b4524dde47e8e3.jpg', 2009, 0000, 'In this sequel to Red Cliff, first minister Cao Cao convinces Emperor Han to initiate a battle against the two Kingdoms of Xu and Wu, who have become allied forces, against all expectations. Red Cliff will be the site for the gigantic battle.', 'In this sequel to Red Cliff, first minister Cao Cao convinces Emperor Han to initiate a battle against the two Kingdoms of Xu and Wu, who have become allied forces, against all expectations. Red Cliff will be the site for the gigantic battle.', '"Улаан эрэг" кино Азид 228 минут үргэлжлэх нэг ангитай гарсан бол Европ болон Америкт хоёр хэсэгт хуваан гаргажээ.', '"Улаан эрэг" киноны үргэлжлэл ангид холбоотны арми хэрхэн хоёр хэсэгт хуваагдаж, ерөнхий сайдын эсрэг хүчин мөхөсдсөн тухай өгүүлнэ. Гэсэн хэдий ч тэд стратегийн уран арга хэрэглэн сайдын хүчийг даван гарахаар төлөвлөнө.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/GTMRFHhdxyY" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt1326972" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1326972/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Red Cliff II (2009) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 142, 13, 'Beijing Film Studio, China Film Group, Lion Rock Productions', 'John Woo', 'John Woo, Khan Chan', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/redclifffilm', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Red_Cliff_%28film%29', '2009-11-20', 'To