(401, 'movie', 'action;adventure;fantasy', 'Shanghai Knights', 'Шанхайгийн Баатрууд', 'shanghai-knights-2003', '201412', '79fadbc9e5c00abac9ca574c8aadf43f9a1d0e2c.jpg', 2003, 0000, 'When a Chinese rebel murders Chon''s estranged father and escapes to England, Chon and Roy make their way to London with revenge on their minds.', 'When a Chinese rebel murders Chon''s estranged father and escapes to England, Chon and Roy make their way to London with revenge on their minds. Chon''s sister, Lin, has the same idea, and uncovers a worldwide conspiracy to murder the royal family but almost no one will believe her', 'Хятадын нэгэн босогч Чонны эцгийг хөнөөж, Англи улс руу зугтаана. Энэ босогчийг барихаар Чонн, Рой хоёр Лондонд ирнэ.', 'Чонны дүү Лин ч бас түүний адил эцгийнхээ өшөөг авч, эзэн хааны гэр бүлд заналхийлсэн дээрэмчинг барих төлөвлөгөөтэй байдаг. Харамсалтай бүсгүйд хэн ч үл итгэнэ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/a26E5JR4M4A" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur54029171" data-title="tt0300471" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0300471/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Shanghai Knights (2003) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 114, 13, 'Touchstone Pictures, Spyglass Entertainment, Birnbaum / Barber Productions', 'David Dobkin', 'Alfred Gough,Miles Millar', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Shanghai-Knights-/121966477843243', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shanghai_Knights', '2003-02-07', 'Jackie Chan, Owen Wilson, Fann Wong |', '', 0, 0, 0